zhe jiang de qing yin jin
liang fang mei shi xiao che an quan xi shu gao
zuo yi qiang du
mei ge zuo wei shang jun zhuang you an quan dai
zai shi yan zhong xin jing guo lian chui shi yan
que bao wai li zhuang ji shi
zuo yi bu hui chan sheng bian xing
zuo yi cai liao
quan bu cai yong zu ran ji bie wei
ji de mian liao
da huo ji wu fa dian ran
shang xia che zi dong pai zhao zhuang zhi
de qing ban xiao che te bie ding zhi
que bao xiao xue sheng an quan wang fan
nan dou zhou kan ji zhe
shen ding zhe jiang de qing bao dao she ying
wei yu hang zhou yi bei
li shu yu hu zhou shi
zong ren kou hai bu dao
liang chang zhuo bi zi de fang mei shi xiao che
de qing yi ye cheng ming
chang bi zi de mei shi xiao che
wang luo shang de ren kan wen ti
zen me shuo ne
hao xiang zhe xiao gu niang zhen piao liang
zhi kan dao liao biao mian
de qing xian jiao yu ju ji wei shu ji
mian dui wang shang pu tian gai di de zan yu
huan huan shuo dao
luo yong chang shang ren gai zhi wei
di yi jian da shi jiu shi xue sheng jiao tong bao zhang gong cheng
liang zhuan shu xiao che
zhou sui yi xia dang di xiao xue sheng de shang xia xue jie song ren wu
suo min gong zi di xue xiao
liang xiao che yi jing yun di de qing xian
liang chan pin dai hao wei
de chang bi zi mei shi xiao che
liang mei shi xiao che
hai wei jiao fu
zhi suo yi bei cheng wei mei shi xiao che
shi yin wei qi jie jian le mei guo xiao che de jing dian zao xing
gong jiao che shen
zai she ji zhi chu
wo men shu ci dui zheng zhou da xue xi ya si xue yuan gou zhi de liang tai mei guo xiao che jin xing yan jiu
bing jie jian le mei guo de xiao che biao zhun
yu tong xiao che chan pin jing li gai yu long jie shao
zhe kuan zhuan ye xiao che
kuai tou bu xiao
qi di pan shang you liang tiao
you che wei guan chuan zhi bao xian gang chu
zai zhong di su jia shi shi
ji hu lao bu ke po
zuo yi quan bu cai yong zu ran ji bie wei
ji de mian liao
yong da huo ji wu fa dian ran

que bao zai zhuang ji shi bu hui bian xing
you yu zhong zhong te shu she ji

zheng bei zhi liang
bai gong li you hao
jia ge gui le
jiu hua fei le
zai de qing zhi qian
zhi you guang dong mou suo gui zu xue xiao ceng gou mai shi yong
huan ge lun tai jiu yao yi qian duo kuai
zhe ge xiao che shi ge shao qian de jia huo
chen guo hua shi yong an xue sheng jiao tong guan li fu wu you xian gong si de zong jing li
ta yi bian zou jin xiao che nei

yin wei ta mi feng xing gao
yi ban de qi che yi nian kai

zhan zai yi pang kan re nao de lu ren men tiao kan qi lai

mei you pai chan

de qing yu cai xue xiao

gong you xue sheng
qi zhong xu yao cheng zuo xiao che de shi
sui zhe xia ke ling sheng xiang qi

zai zhao guan yuan de dai ling xia

dan wo gan jue

de xue sheng xian lu

kao bei ye te bie ai

ming xue sheng hou

bao dao kan fa hou
yin qi le she hui de guang fan guan zhu
mei guo ge lun bi ya guo ji xue yuan zai yan yuan zi yuan da sha
ceng ban gong di dian de biao pai ye bei qu zou

bing tan le ta dui zhe yi xian xiang de kan fa

bing wei ci zhi fu le jin
wan yuan de bao ming fei he xue fei

ren da de fa zhan mo shi zuo wei yi zhong tan suo
bei hang ye ren shi suo guan zhu
dan shen zhen geng duo de fu li ji gou gui mo jiao xiao
zi jin fang mian jun bu ju bei shi li
wu fa zuo dao chang qi de gao tou ru
yi xie fu li ji gou cong xiao gui mo zuo qi
xun qiu gun dong shi fa zhan de mo shi
zhe fang mian zuo de jiao hao de shi jing xi yang yi yang yuan
zuo wei shen zhen shi wei yi ying li de fu li ji gou

xiao chu ying xiang

yao qiu xie chun yan he

zhi yu ru he bei yan bian cheng hei she hui
he dang di da hei chu e de zheng zhi ren wu you guan
sheng li you guan bu men ceng zai hui yi shang gong kai pi ping xia men da hei bu li
xia men shi jue ding jia da da hei chu e de li du
qi zhong bao kuo jiang da hei ban sheng ji zhe yang de ji zhi chuang xin
xia men dang di mei ti de yi pian ming wei
xia men da ji hei e shi li bu xian shan lu shui huo quan guo da hei ban ken ding
de bao dao zhong cheng
you yu shi wei
shi zheng fu gao du zhong shi
shi da hei ban de liu ming gong zuo ren yuan
fen bie lai zi fa yuan
wu jing he si fa liu ge bu men
xiang bi er yan
quan guo qi ta di fang de da hei bu men
tong chang zhi shi gong an ji guan xia de yi ge jian zhi ji gou
xia men shi zi ren wei zhe yang de ling huo ji zhi zai quan guo ling xian
dan ta men hu shi de shi
ben ying zuo wei zhong li jue se de fa yuan ye jia ru da hei ban
zhe zhong xie tong ban an mo shi yu du li shen pan yuan ze xiang bei
zao yi shou dao zhi yi
da hei shi yi xiang zheng zhi ren wu
xia men shi gong an ju de yi ming gong zuo ren yuan tou lu
mei feng dang di chu xian ju zhong dou ou
xun xin zi shi deng e xing shi jian
gong an bu men dou xu shang bao zhi shi da hei ban
da hei ban li ke jie ru
zai qian shu de dang di mei ti bao dao zhong
xia men shi da hei ban fu zhu ren zhong hua yong jiu biao shi
yao da zao da xiao
lou tou jiu da
bi xu ba ta men xiao mie zai meng ya zhong
ji zhi gong de er shen bian hu ren
bei jing shi de heng lv shi shi wu suo lv shi lin wei ren wei
cong she hei fan zui de gou cheng yao jian fen xi
ji zhi gong deng ren fan zui bu gou cheng hei she hui xing zhi zu zhi fan zui
xia men si fa bu men dui hei she hui zu zhi de ren ding
yi jiang di dao yi ban fan zui tuan huo de biao zhun le
zai long xi cun
bu shao jia ting xian ru le qian suo wei you de kun jing
you yu liang ge er zi ji zhi gong
ji qin li de bei bu
ji jian tong yi jia de ji ben sheng huo
zhi neng yi kao er xi zai cheng li zuo xiao shi gong zhi cheng
sui de er zi zai ye bu gan zhu zai jia li
ta lao jue de you ren yao na qiang lai da wo men
ta hai bu gan shang xue
pa bei chao xiao wei hei she hui de er zi
ling wai yi ming she an zhe ji song he de qi zi diu xia liang sui de er zi
da suan li hun
jia shu men dan xin
ta men chu yu hou
ru he mian dui ban sui yi sheng de hei she hui zui ming
geng duo de ren jue de
zhe shi yi jian yao yuan de shi qing
ta men de xing qi hen chang
chu lai de shi hou bu zhi dao zen me yang ne
er ji jiang dao lai de er shen
jiang jue ding ta men de ming yun
ru he kan dai nv xing hao shen cai yu shi ye zhi jian de guan xi
yi shi ye xian xing rong nv xing xiong bu de ru gou
ci shuo fa yuan zi yu xiang gang yu le xin wen
xing rong nv yi ren kao hao shen cai xi yin guan zhong mu guang
gong zuo liang ye yin ci zeng jia
bu guo zhe yi zhong shuo fa you xiang gang chuan zhi tai wan hou
que zai tai wan zheng tan yin fa xuan ran da bo
na me nin ren wei
dui nv xing lai shuo zhe yi shuo fa shi fou qian tuo
zai nin kan lai
shi ye xian de shuo fa shi bu shi di que you wu hua nv xing de yi wei
huan ying nin can yu wo men de tao lun
wo yao liu yan
xing dan zao fei shi shen wang ceng jiang cong fei fang chan liu gei qi yu qian qi nv er
ben kan ji zhe zai fei shi za che de di dian dun le liang tian fa xian
cong pao shi tou de jiao du
gen ben kan bu jian lai wang de che
zhe ge wu liao de e yi you xi
zhi shi gen ju you yuan ji jin de ma da sheng
wang gao su lu shang pao shi zi
liang liang shen zhen pai zhao yue ye che
yi qian yi hou shi li pian yi hai xian zha dui de hai feng e bu zhen
zai gao su lu shang shi xiang shen zhen
er shi tou ling cun de shao nian men
cha bu duo li kai tai qiu an zi
qian wang gao su lu bian gang an zhuang le chang ming lu deng de hui lan an qian wan shua
huang xi jian he lin you quan kai xin di yi shi zi ji zhong le di si liang che
liang tian hou ta men bei bu shi hai mang ran bu zhi zi ji hai si le xing dan
ta zuo jia xia fang dong mai bei shi kuai ci chuan
fen zhong hou song da yi yuan shi tong kong yi jing kuo san
xing dan de mu yang yi dian ye mei you bian
wu hei de chang fa yong pi jin bang zai er hou
yi fu shi dan diao de su se
ming liang er mei li de su yan
nian sheng dan jie ta dai li wu dao li zi ji jia bu yuan de she qu zhu can dian he lao ren
hai zi wan you xi
ding zhuo hong se sheng dan mao la zhuo yi qun ren pai shou chang ge
hai xiao de na me kai xin
zhe ge ben yi kuai yao dan chu gong zhong shi ye de nv zi
yin yi wai si wang
zai ci cheng wei bei ju nv zhu jue
ta huo hua na tian
shen zhen shi chu xian le zi fa de shang qian ren song zang dui wu
dian shi tai he guang bo dou zhuan bo le zhui dao hui
jiao jing bei pai wang bin yi guan jin xing ren qun shu dao
ta liu zai gong zhong yin xiang li de yong yuan shi
nian xia tian de yang zi
liang ge yue shi jian
ta gen zhe zhong yang wen ming ban zu de yi ge tuan dao quan guo ge di can yu cong fei xian jin shi ji bao gao hui
na nian ta bu guo
gang gang shi qu le zhang fu cong fei
bing liu xia le yi ge bu man zhou sui de ying er
qu ming xing xiao cong fei
dang shi zai bao gao tuan li
hai you yi ge jiao yan yu qing qing de miao zu nv hai
shi cong fei he xing dan liang kou zi zi zhu de
ge gui zhou sheng bi jie xian shao shu min zu xue sheng de dai biao
yi zhi juan kuan zi zhu pin kun xue sheng de cong fei
bu jin ba zi ji de yan chu suo de dou juan gei le ge zhong gong yi shi ye
bing qie gao diao chu xian zai suo you wu tai shang
nian xian cha chu ai zheng wan qi
ran hou bei ping xuan shang gan dong zhong guo
bing zai she hui cheng song zhong zou wan le ren sheng zhi lu
ci hou xing dan jiu ji cheng le ta de yi gong hao
ta mo mo di ji xu gei cong fei zi zhu de ren men ji qian
dan zai bao gao hui hou jiu tui chu le gong zhong shi ye
hai you yi ge bu wei wai ren zhi de jue ding shi
xing dan jiang cong fei ming xia wei yi de cai chan
yi tao you yi wei qi ye jia bang zhu hai wan le dai kuan de fang zi
xie zai le cong fei yu qian qi de nv er ming xia
zi ji he xiao ying er zhu zai yi tao zheng fu ti gong de zhi you ju zhu quan de pu tong gao ceng zhu zhai lou li
quan guo you dian shi ji de di fang du hui dui zhe dui kang li you xie yin xiang
shi tou ling ren que shi li wai
zhi dao jing cha zai
ri lai dao cun li

wan quan mei you you ren

zhe ge di fang de da ming jiao dong keng yue
shi yi ge gu yi you zhi de di ming

shi tou ling ye fa sheng le liang jian da shi

zui xiao yi ge jiao lin you quan

yi xiang wo xing wo su

nian wo he cong fei yi qi qu gui zhou
na shi ta dai zhuo dan dan

qu le jiu bao zhuo xiao hai zi ku
ta ye shi na shi qi cai che di jie shou le cong fei
he cong fei ren shi shi ji nian de liu jia zeng shuo
ta men dou xiang yong wei bo de li liang gai bian na pa yi ge ren de ming yun ye hao

de dao le yi ge fu pin ji jin de quan pan jie guan

hai gu li ta

jin ru shi tou ling xiao xue hou

xie zi de sheng chan zhong xin

gang gou wen bao

ye zuo yi gong
ta ling yi jian jian chi de shi qing shi jia ban
ta zong jue de zi ji shi jie zhuo cong fei de ming zi cai dang shang de gong wu yuan
suo yi zai jiao yu ju ta shi chu ming de zui wan zou de ren
zi ji de gong zuo jia bei
bie ren de gong zuo ye na guo lai bang zhuo zuo
sui ran hai shi shen zhen shi ai xin da shi

ji hu mei you yi yi shuang de cheng wei chu xian zai ren he chang he
shen zhen zhe ge cheng shi de jie zou he qi fen
shi xing dan kai shi le kuai le du li de sheng huo
er zhe ge cheng shi de fu she li que yi ling wai yi zhong fang shi gai bian zhuo xiang cun
nian cong shen zhen dao shan tou de gao su kuai gui xian zai yi jing xiu jian dao liao shi tou ling cun de shang fang

jia zai nong tian jian de ji shi mi gao de shui ni lu mian li liang qiang da

zuo you shi gao su lu
que cheng le ge feng jing mei li de kun ju

zhe xie bian bu la ji

zhu san jiao da gai shi zhong guo gao su gong lu zui fa da de di qu

ye mei you shou piao dian

gan deng di qu

yi jin ru hui dong xian jiu hen jing ya

ji nan shi ren li zi yuan he she hui bao zhang ju fa xian gai shi mou dan wei bao song te shu gong zhong tui xiu de dang an cai liao she xian zao jia
cha chu tui hui she xian zao jia deng bu he gui ding dang an duo da

wo jiu qu wu tong de di fang
jiu mo dao dao le
xia jun feng dou li you yi ba zhe die de xiao shui guo dao
zhe die zhuang tai xia bu dao
da kai ye jin
li mi zuo you
zheng ge dao ren bu dao xia de shou zhi chang
xia jun feng yong zhe ba dao qie xiang chang
shi mei tian yao yong dao de sheng cun gong ju
yi ban dou dai zai shen shang
zai cheng guan da dui qin wu shi
mian dui liang ming shen gao jin
de cheng guan dui yuan
xia jun feng tao chu le ta
yi qie sui zhi wu ke wan hui
jie xia lai fa sheng de yi mu
yi shen pan jue shu you ru xia xu shu
zai gai qin wu qu ban gong shi nei
xia jun feng chi sui shen xie dai de jian dao xian hou lian ci shen kai
zhang xu dong ji zhang wei shu dao
zhi bei hai ren shen kai zuo xiong
bei bu ci chuang
te bie shi zuo xiong bu ci chuang ci po xin zang er dao zhi shi xue xing xiu ke si wang
zhi bei hai ren zhang xu dong quan shen duo chu ci chuang
te bie shi zuo xiong bu shang fang ci chuang ci po zuo fei he xin zang er dao zhi shi xue xing xiu ke si wang

shi jian zhong di shang zhe zhang wei hui yi cheng
ta gang zou jin ban gong shi
kan jian zhe ge nan zi
zhi xia jun feng
bei dui zhuo ta

wo kan qing kuang bu hao

ba ta zhuai dao qiang fu jin
ta hui shou jiu za le wo yi dao

wo jiu pao le

ying yi gu yi shang hai zui zhui jiu xing shi ze ren

bo duo zheng zhi quan li zhong shen

chun wan de men piao bi chun yun de huo che piao geng jin qiao
bing fei suo you lao bai xing dou ru ran shao ping na yang ke pan
chun wan ce hua ren zhu hai gao su nan fang zhou mo ji zhe
tong chang chun wan da ting zhong guan zhong
men piao you chun wan ban gong shi fa fang
dui xiang bao kuo ge ge hang ye dai biao
ji guan ling dao he guang gao ke hu shang
zhu hai ping bing bu ren shi xiao lian ge

wang xiao xiang ji zhe jiang shu le yan jing wen ti gei zi ji dai lai de xin suan
hu nan sheng ping jiang xian ren
mou tian de qing chen
wang xiao zuo qin shu mo tuo che wai chu ban shi
bu shen cong che shang diao xia
zuo lian bu yan zhong ca shang
dang shi quan shen shi xie
shang shi hen yan zhong
wang xiao bei gan dao xian chang de qin shu jiu jin song dao liao ping jiang xian an ding zhen zhong xin yi yuan
jian cheng an ding yi yuan
wang xiao qin shu hui yi
dang shi zai an ding yi yuan yan jing mei mao chu feng le
dang shi yi yuan gen ju wo de shen ti qing kuang
biao shi ke neng you sheng ming wei xian
an ding yi yuan zuo chu ci pan duan de yi ju shi
wang xiao zai jiao tong shi gu qian de
yin wei lao lei guo du
dao zhi da nao que xue
ceng zhu yuan yi ge xing qi
er jin nao bu zai ci shou shang
wu yi zeng jia le zhi liao nan du
yue ban ge duo yue hou

wang xiao jing chang gan jue zuo yan yang
da bai tian zou lu
jing chang shuai jiao

nian ji bu xiao le
zou lu lao shi bu xiao xin
xia tian de yi ge wan shang
wang xiao yu peng you wan shi li you xi
dang wang xiao zhe zhuo you yan kan dong xi shi
wang xiao di yi ci fa xian zi ji zuo yan shi li xia jiang de ru ci li hai
zhe yi xi jie
wang xiao lian xiang dao liao
zi ji lao shi shuai jiao
ke neng yu zuo yan shi li xia jiang you guan
zhi yan zhi tong

zhi liao qi jian
yi sheng que zhen wei yan nei you yi wu

hua qu fei yong

hou jing zhuan jia fu zhen

sui hou de yi nian duo shi jian nei

ban sui zhuo zhi liao

yan qiu bian xiao

wo men jiu bu gai bang li jing e chu ju zhe ge zheng ming
er qie he shi shen fen zhe jian shi qing
na hai de dao dang di gong an ji guan jin xing
gong an yi jing gei ta men kai le shen fen zheng ming le
jiu zai ji zhe fa gao qian
li jing e lai dian hua gao zhi
wen ti yi jing de dao jie jue
cheng yong zhen de xue li yi jing bei zhu xiao
ji zhe cong qi qi ha er da xue zi dong hua zhuan ye xue ji ke liao jie dao
hei long jiang sheng jiao yu ting yi jing tong guo wang luo gao zhi xue xiao
tong xing ming tong shen fen zheng hao de xue sheng yi jing qing li wan le
li jing e bi ye yi bu zai shi wen ti
mao ming shang da xue bei hou de na xie lou dong
jin kao xing zheng chu fa que fa wei she li
zi luo cai xia shi jian yi lai
lu xu pu chu duo qi mao ming shang da xue shi jian
qing xing ge bu yi yang
you zai quan li yun zuo xia ding ti de
you shuang fang mo xu de
xi nan zheng fa da xue fa xue yuan jiao shou xu jing cun fen xi ren wei
mao ming shang da xue shi jian lv you fa sheng
shuo dao di hai shi ren men fan zui ya li bu da
zhe xie ren bu shi mei you fa lv yi shi
bu shi bu zhi dao yao dong fa shou fa
er shi ren men da duo ren wei
zhe bu xiang sha ren qiang jie tou dong xi na me xing zhi e lie
jiao yu bu wei le zhi zhi kao shi wu bi
yue fa bu le
guo jia jiao yu kao shi wei gui chu li ban fa
gai fa gui de zhu yao mu di shi cheng zhi kao shi zuo bi
er bu shi xian shi zhong ye hen yan zhong de zhao sheng fu bai
jiu you xiao xi cheng
cao an yi jin ru zui hou wan shan jie duan
dan zhi jin wu guo
cao an zhuan jia zu zu zhang
xu jing cun gao su ji zhe
cheng yong zhen he li jing e de xing wei wei fan xiang guan gui ding
dan shi bu she ji wei fa
wo guo xian zai hai mei you zhuan men de zhen dui sheng xue kao shi zhong di wei fa xing wei jin xing chu fa de fa lv
jiao yu quan bei qin zhan gai ru he chu zhi ye que fa xiang guan de fa lv fa gui
dui yu mao ming ding ti shang da xue zhe lei shi jian
zhi neng tong guo zai zhe xie shi jian zhong di qi ta xiang guan de wei fa xing wei lai jin xing cheng chu
yi luo cai xia shi jian wei li
yuan hu nan sheng long hui xian gong an ju min jing wang zheng rong
mao ming zhe wang jia jun zhi fu bei hu nan sheng shao yang shi bei ta qu ren min fa yuan
yi wei zao guo jia ji guan zheng jian zui pan chu you qi tu xing liang nian
yu yuan fan shou hui zui suo pan chu de you qi tu xing
nian xing fa shi xing shu zui bing fa
jue ding zhi xing you qi tu xing
er qi ta li ru zhao ban bu men
xue xiao suo shou dao de xing zheng huo zhe dang ji chu fen jin xian yu liu dang cha kan
kai chu dang ji
xian you she an ren yuan bei chu xing shi chu fa
hu ji guan li bu men cai shi guan jian guan kou

xu jing cun ren wei
xian xing lu qu ti zhi ti gong le bian li
ji zhe ceng she xiang
ke neng ru tong luo cai xia shi jian yi yang
zhe jian ding ti shi jian cang zhuo zhong duo quan li de lan yong
dan xian shi chu hu ji zhe yi liao
mao ming zhe he bei mao ming zhe dou lai zi pu tong jia ting
cheng yong zhen de fu mu wu nong
qi jie jie ye zhi shi ge pu tong de jia ting fu nv
xiang li jing e zhe zhong qing kuang
cong biao mian kan shi chu yu wu zhi
ta bu zhi dao zhe me zuo de hou guo
dan cong zheng ti lai kan
mao ming shang da xue shi jian pin pin fa sheng
gen yuan zai yu mu qian de ji hua lu qu ti zhi
gao deng jiao yu wen ti yan jiu xue zhe
shi ji jiao yu yan jiu yuan xiong bing qi wei ren wei
cong gao kao dao zhao sheng zhe ge lian tiao shi hen cui ruo de
ru guo yi ge huan jie neng gou da tong
hou mian de huan jie jiu ke yi ceng ceng da tong
xiong bing qi shuo
xian zai xue sheng na dao yi ge tong zhi shu
jiu ke yi gai bian zi ji de shen fen
wu lun ni shi bu shi ding ti de
yi qian cheng ji he neng li ru he
dou ke yi hen qing song di wan cheng shen fen de zhuan bian
jin er wan cheng ming yun de zhuan bian
zhe zhong xian zhuang
shi de zhong duo mei you neng li kao qu da xue huo zhe hao da xue de ren
zou shang le zuo bi
mao ming de dao lu
xiong bing qi shuo
ru guo she ding de da xue jiao yu zhi du shi ru ou mei guo jia de kuan jin yan chu
na me jiu bu hui you ren zheng po tou pi lai mao ming ding ti le
ni ji bian jin lai le
dan shi ni yi ran ke neng shi yi ge mei you shen fen de ren
ni hai mian lin zhuo bi ye zhe ge kan er
cheng xin que shi shi gen yuan
nan kai da xue she hui gong zuo yu she hui zheng ce xi zhu ren
zhong guo she hui gong zuo jiao yu xie hui fu hui zhang guan xin ping ze jiang ci lei wen ti zhi zhi she hui cheng xin
zhe hai shi fan ying le zhong guo de yi ge lao wen ti
zhe me duo nian mei you jian li qi lai yi ge cheng xin ti xi
guan xin ping shuo
hen duo shi hou
bu cheng xin de xing wei bing mei you shang hai dao te ding ren de li yi
er shi sun hai zheng ge she hui de gong zhong li yi
cheng yong zhen jie yong li jing e de gao kao cheng ji qu shang le da xue
ru guo bu shi bi ye shi chu xian wen ti
na me ta kan si mei you sun hai shui de li yi
shi ji shang que shi zhan yong le ta bu gai zhan yong de jiao yu zi yuan
sun hai qi ta ren de shou jiao yu de quan li
jiu cheng yong zhen mao li jing e zhi ming shang da xue yi shi
guan xin ping ren wei shi yi ge dian xing de she hui bu cheng xin
you que fa dui bu cheng xin de cheng jie ji zhi de li zi
yi fang mian shi guan li zhe de cheng xin
dui she hui bu fu ze ren
bu zuo hao xin xi de he dui gong zuo rang mao ming ding ti zhe qing er yi ju di zuan le lou dong
ling yi fang mian shi she hui wen hua de cheng xin
ren men zai hang wei yi shi zhong dui zhe ge wen ti kan de bu yan zhong
wang wang zhi kan yi ge ren de cheng gong
que bu kan ta shi zen me cheng gong de
bu kan ta zai cheng gong de dao lu shang shi fou you qi pian deng bu dao de de xing wei
yi ge ren tai cheng xin que bei cheng zuo tai lao shi
bu gou ling huo

que hui bei ren wei shi you ben shi
zheng ge she hui wen hua zhong
ren men dui zhe lei cheng xin wen ti de ping jia dou shi niu qu de

ming shi le zai gao kao zhong wei gui de dai jia

ru guo jin jin dui kao sheng hui qi jing shi da bang
er wu fa zai geng wei shen guang de she hui ling yu shi xian dui quan li shi fan xing wei de gui zhi

wan dao shang po lu duan shi
che liang zhuang dao dao lu you ce de bo xing hu lan
wen hua dang chang si wang
che liang ji bo xing hu lan ye yan zhong shou sun

reng wu fa jie tong

che qian fang de bu yuan chu
ji jian chang fang he ji gen yan cong zai lv se de tian ye zhong ge wai xian yan
ci xing de zui zhong song huo di dian
jiang men shi he yuan suan na chang
yi jing jin zai yan qian
ge xiao shi de zou zou ting ting

guo lu fei cong
yi ye jian de yun fei mei dun
yuan zuo you ji suan

jue da duo shu da guan che dou shi chao zai che liang
qi ta xiao che kai zai zhou wei yi ding yao fei chang xiao xin

ta men shou wo cong ye zi ge zheng

yi kai shi jiu lian mang shuo le hao ji ge
ran hou gao su wo men bin guan de di zhi
dang wo men zhao dao na ge bin guan hou
wo men ji mang jin ru chu shi de
fa xian wang yan shang shen chi luo
xia shen chuan le tiao nei ku
nei ku he chuang dan shang du shi jing ye
ju wang yan fu mu jiang shu
shi fa qian yi tian wan shang
wang yan zuo wei wu xi ke ji zhi ye xue yuan
yi xia jian cheng gai xiao
tuan wei fu shu ji
zai qi zhi jie ling dao zhang zi wen de yao qiu xia
chu xi le you gai xiao zuo wei zhu ban fang de zai xi gao xiao tuan wei yan tao hui wan yan
dang shi gai xiao yu wang yan yi tong chu xi de ren yuan hai you zhang zi wen
shi ren gai xiao tuan wei shu ji
shi ren gai xiao tuan wei gan shi
zhi wu bu xiang
shi hou wang yan hui yi
na tian de yan xi shang zi ji zhi he le liang xiao bei bai jiu
bu zhi wei he bian gan dao quan shen fa li
zhi zhi bei ren dai jin bin guan shi bao shi dou wu li fan kang
dui yu shi bao de ren
wang yan zhi chu
zheng shi xue xiao ju ban wan yan suo zai fan dian de lao ban
shuo dao shang xin chu
wang yan de fu mu chong man ao hui
wo men de nv er bi ye yu shou du ti yu da xue
ceng shi yi ming tai quan dao yun dong yuan
zai dan ren gai xiao tuan wei fu shu ji zhi qian
ceng ren zhi gai xiao ti yu lao shi
an li lai shuo
yi ta de shen shou
shi bu ke neng rang shi bao zhe de cheng de
wo men huai yi na tian he de jiu you wen ti
dang wen ji wei he zai nv er zao dao xing qin fan hou mei you ji shi bao an shi
wang yan fu qin wang zheng nan tong xin di gao su wo men
bu shi wo men bu dong fa
yu dao zhe yang de shi qing
wo men dang ran zhi dao ying gai bao an
dan wo men yi jia dou shi si xiang bao shou de lao bai xing
zi ji de nv er zuo wei yi ge wei chu jia de da gu niang
yu dao le zhe zhong shi qing
rang wo men zen me shuo
kuang qie wang yan xing ge gang lie
ru guo ci shi chuan yang chu qu
ta shi wu lun ru he ye jie shou bu liao de
yao shi dang shi bao jing
shuo bu ding ta zao jiu si le
wu xing de si xiang jia suo
rang zhe ge jia ting zai mian dui qu ru shi
zui zhong xuan ze le chen mo
dui yu zhe ci bei qiang bao de jing li
wang yan fu mu cai qu de suo wei bu jiu cuo shi jing ran shi
reng diao nv er dang tian suo chuan de nei yi nei ku
bing rang wang yan fu xia le yi pian jin ji bi yun yao
er zheng shi ci ju
dao zhi le mu qian jing fang qu zheng ji wei kun nan de ju mian
ci ci bei qiang bao de jing li
gei wang yan dai lai le ji da de xin ling shang hai
shi fa hou wang yan ceng ku zhuo pao dao xue xiao ren shi bu men
yao qiu ci qu zi ji xiao tuan wei fu shu ji yi zhi
tong shi hui fu qi ti yu lao shi de zhi wu
dui yu wang yan de ci zhi ju dong
wang yan de jia shu zai jie shou cai fang shi biao shi
gai xiao you qiang po nv lao shi pei jiu de chuan tong
wo men huai yi xue xiao ling dao zui chu jiang wang yan cong ti yu jiao xue bu tiao zhi tuan wei jiu shi bie you yong xin
wo men de nv er ben lai bu yuan yi jie shou qu tuan wei de diao ren
dan xiao fang ren shi bu men ceng yi zai zhao ta tan hua
hou lai shen zhi yin yin tou lu chu
bu yao jing jiu bu chi chi fa jiu
zai zhe zhong qing kuang xia
wang yan bu de bu jie shou diao ren
dan zi cong qu le tuan wei zhi hou
ta jiu mo ming qi miao bian de hen mang
jing chang hen wan hui jia
zhe qi zhong you tuan wei wai lian gong zuo fang mian de zhu duo ying chou yuan yin
hai you jiu shi ling dao de ke yi diao nan
cai fang zhong wang yan jia shu hai tou lu
zhang zi wen zuo wei wang yan de zhi jie ling dao
jing chang zai lin jin xia ban zhi shi
gei wang yan lin shi bu zhi ren wu
tan dao wang yan zhi qian de yi ci ge wan zi sha jing li
wang yan de mu qin lao lei zong heng
wo men de hai zi tai shan liang ye tai tian zhen le
na ci zao yu qiang bao zhi hou
ta de di yi ge dian hua bing bu shi da gei wo men
er shi da gei le ta dang shi de nan peng you yang mou
yang mou zai de zhi le ta de zao yu hou
bian jian jian kai shi leng luo ta
wang yan wei le wan hui er ren de guan xi
hai ceng yi du qian wang yang mou de lao jia he nan qu zhao ta
dan zui zhong que shi yi ge ren ku zhuo hui lai de
na zhi hou mei duo jiu
wang yan jiu you le di yi ci de ge wan zi sha ju dong
xing hao bei wo men fa xian bing ji shi zu zhi
na ci zhi hou
wo men ye song ta qu jie shou guo jing shen he xin li fang mian de zhi liao
mei xiang dao shi ge yi nian
ta hai shi xuan ze le zhe tiao lu
cong wang yan jia shu ti gong gei jing fang de cai liao shang ke yi kan chu
wang yan de fu mu ren wei
ri de bei qin fan shi jian

er zuo wei na ci wan yan de zu zhi zhe
wu xi ke ji zhi ye xue yuan dui wang yan shou dao de shang hai fu you bu ke tui xie de ze ren

qiang po yi shuo bing bu cun zai

qi gong zuo ren yuan ou er you ying chou shi nan mian de

wang yan zai yu xue sheng de jiao tan zhong ye duo ci biao xian chu dui ci gong zuo de fan gan
ceng dan ren gai xiao xue sheng hui zhu xi de lin mou

yi bian shi shi yan shi xin zi cheng fu jia zi di
yi tian shi jian
zhe yi shi jian xun su cheng wei mei ti guan zhu de jiao dian
wo xiang wen yi xia
guang zhou ri bao
zui zao shi zen me guan zhu dao zhe ge shi qing
guang zhou ri bao
qi shi ye shi shi jin quan
jin quan shao xia
da wo men de bao liao re xian
ken ding you lian xi hao ji jia mei ti
da bao liao re xian guo qu de
ni bu xiang zhui jiu na ge ren dui ni de yi xie qi pian
bu xiang zhui jiu
mei you yi si
xie nv shi de kuan rong
jia ting de bu xing
rang ren men dui wang you fu jia zi di you le geng duo de fen nu zhi qing
ran er jiu zai zuo tian
you wang you bao liao
suo wei de guang zhou de fu jia zi di gen ben jiu shi yi ge wang luo tui shou
ta de ling yi ge shen fen shi jin quan shao xia
mou wang luo lun tan de ban zhu
you zhe zi ji de ce hua ying xiao wang zhan
wang zhan shang he nan
yi ju jiang shi jian
xiao yue yue shi jian
dou shi qi dui wai xuan chuan de jing dian an li
zhe qi zhong jiu bao kuo mu qin gui pa qian mi jiu nv er de zhi xing ce hua fang an
jiu zai xie nv shi gui di qiu juan kuan shi jian chu xian qian yi tian
zhe fen wan zheng de ce hua fang an jiu yi jing bei gua zai le wang zhan shang
jin quan shao xia
wo kan dao zhe ge tie zi ye shi dang pu tong tie lai kan
bing mei you zen me qu li hui
dan shi hou lai wo gan jue zhe ge mu qin
ta nv er de qing kuang hen rang wo jiu xin
ran hou wo lian xi ta zhi hou ne
wo jiu gen ta shuo le yi xia
shuo wo de xiang fa
tong guo shen me fang shi lai bang zhu ta
ni jue de xiang bu xiang shi tong yi ge ren ne
wo zen me zhi dao
shuo shen me chao zuo

gao dao wo tou dou yun le
jin quan shao xia
zai wo ge ren de wang luo chuan bo xue yan jiu dang zhong
qi fen shi bi jiao rong yi yin qi guan zhu de
er qie hui zai da fan wei de chuan bo
suo yi shuo shi bi bu de yi cai yong zhe yi zhao

gan xie da jia
ta ye bu zai xu yao re xin ren de juan zhu

dan ta xiang mei ti biao shi
sheng ming bi dao de zhong yao
ta bing bu hou hui
ru jin mian dui zhe yang yi ge ce hua chu lai de shi jian
mian dui yi chang rang ren wu wei za cheng de chao zuo
zhe ge yang ben zhi de hao hao pou xi
zhe ge wang luo ce hua ren de jing xin ce hua zui hou cheng gong le
ni jue de ta shi zuo le yi jian hao shi ma
bai yan song ping lun yuan
wo jue de xian zai zhe dui mu nv liang yi ran shi rang ren jue de ke lian
dan shi wang luo ce hua shi fen ke wu
xi li hu tu can yu qi zhong de mei ti mei diao cha zhen xiang
qi shi dang le wang luo ce hua de bang xiong
rang ren gan jue ke xi
dan shi shou zhe yang de shi qing ying xiang
wo men she hui de xin ren wei ji ye xu hui jin yi bu jia ju

huan yuan yi bu yuan yi shen chu yuan shou
jiu bian de ke yi

wo bu hou hui
yin wei wo jiu le yi ming
zai sheng ming mian qian
dao de ke yi xi sheng
lei si zhe yang de dong xi

zhan bu zhu jiao

jiu gen lang lai le de gu shi yi yang

geng duo de ren jiu hui tui que

ni shuo ta shi bang le ren
hai shi hai le zhe ge she hui

pin kun di qu e lie de

qian mian hai shi wang wo shen shang kan
dan shi wei chen yi jing yong li tui zhuo long shi xu
liang ren xiang chi de li dao ji shi die luo chuang xia ye yi ran bao chi
wei chen tang zai di shang
zuo shou li yi zhi wo zhuo dao bu fang
long shi xu zuo zai ta shen shang
dao jian zai wei chen zuo jian shang you hua xia liang ge hen chang de yuan xing dao kou
wo si ming di tui ta
ba ta tui dao le
wo jiu gan jin bei zhuan shen
qu kai su she de men
su she men ping shi bing bu fan suo
zhi you yi ge cha xiao
yi ba jiu ke yi kai men
dan shi wei chen hai zai mo suo cha xiao de shi hou
zuo jian you ai le yi dao
shang kou da gai you
zhe yi dao hai bu suan zui zhong
yin wei wo zhong yu ba men da kai
you shou yi kai men
ta xiang wo de you jian bang
you hen hen di kan le yi dao
yin wei wei chen dou zai pao de zhuang tai
dao kou sui ran shen er chang
que dou mei you shang dao jin gu
wei chen yi zhi ting dao yi zhong qi guai de sheng yin
cong hao jin de chuang shang chuan lai
sheng yin hen da
you dian xiang shui kai le
you xiang shi wang shui li chui qi
pu tu tu de sheng yin
wei chen gan jue si hu you ren qi chuan bu shang lai
zhe shi ta hai bu zhi dao hao jin yi jing bei ge kai le hou guan
zhi shi pin ming di xiang
dan yuan zi ji hao peng you de su she pao qu
yi lu shang xue ji qing xi
dan dang shi lou dao li yi pian hei
zhi you lou wai de gong di chuan guo lai de yi dian zhao ming guang
lin yue he li liang zhe shi cai cong meng zhong jing xing
ni gao lang zi me
lin yue zai shang pu dui long shi xu han
wai mian gong di de guang yin yin yue yue zhao jin lai
wo neng kan jian long shi xu zhan zhuo
ta hen ping jing di shuo bu guan ni de shi
sui shou na le yi ge shen me

jiu chu qu le
ta shuo hua sheng yin hen ping wen

yin wei ta men shui ye mei shuo hua
wo jiu kan jian long shi xu chu qu le
yin wei long shi xu de fan ying
lin yue jue de you ren zuo e meng er yi
zhe shi hou lin yue tu ran gan dao
jiu zai zi ji de chuang tou shang fang
hao jin cheng zhuo chuang lan gan

quan shi shi de

zhe cai kan jian hao jin yi jing pa dao zai di shang
xie zai pen chu lai
sheng yin hen da

zhi you ta men yi ge qin shi zai
deng dao li xue wei

ta yi zhi zhi zhuo zi ji de hou long
hao xiang shuo hen tong ku

xue xiao li hen hei

hao jin shen shang bing mei you duo yu de shang

zhong yi yuan he xue xiao jiu zai ge bi

yi sheng chu lai shuo
hou guan shi guan dou bei ge kai le

dang shi na le ge dan zi chu lai

hen kuai lai le liang ge jing cha
jing cha wen wo men

wo men na zhi dao
zhen de yi dian ye ting bu dao
wo men dang shi ye bu zhi dao shi long shi xu sha de ren
ta hai hui da le wo yi ju bu guan wo shi

ta yi jing pao le da gai you
fen zhong zuo you le

fa zhi zhou bao
tong xun yuan luo ming mei
hu nan sheng xin huang dong zu zi zhi xian gong an ju yi she xian gu yi shang hai zhi si zui jiang fan zui xian yi ren yang hai yang

yi fa xiang jian cha yuan ti qing dai bu
yi qi fa sheng zai
nian qian de ji ming an zhen po zhong jie

xin huang gong an ju jie dao bao jing
gai xian cha ping xiang tang jiao cun cun min yang guo xian bei ren sha hai
gai xian xing zhen bu men ji ji kai zhan gong zuo
zui hou que ding si zhe de zhi er yang hai yang you zhong da zuo an xian yi
dan yang an fa hou qu xiang bu ming
gai xian xing zhen da dui yi zhi mei you fang song dui ci an de zhen po gong zuo
dan yang hai yang ru shi chen da hai
yao wu yin xin

xin huang gong an ju xing zhen min jing yi kai men ping jing da zou fang wei qi ji
zhen mi zhen cha
fen xi xian suo
tong guo shen ru qun zhong

bing zai zhe jiang wen zhou huo che zhan fu jin gong di shang chu xian guo
de dao xian suo hou

bing cong quan ju chou diao jing yan feng fu

yi xia huo che

zheng fu you yi wu gei you ke yi ge hao de gou wu huan jing
chang lian biao shi
yao che di jie jue dao you you dao you ke gou wu ti qu ju e yong jin wen ti
yi fang mian xu yin ru dao you gong zi zhi du
bao zhang dao you shou ru
ling wai yi fang mian xu zhan duan dao you ti qu ju e yong jin de wen chuang
jian li gong shang
zhi jian deng duo bu men de lian he zhi fa bu men
zong he zhi li gou wu huan jing
yi ge li hao de xiao xi shi
quan guo shou ge dao you ri zai zhang jia jie zheng shi dan sheng
zhang jia jie quan ti zhu ce dao you yuan huo de le xu bao
yi yuan ren sheng yi wai shang hai xian

zhe shi yi ge hao de xin hao

te yue ji zhe ye yi fa zi yun nan li jiang
shi jie guan jun
dang te shu de shen fen zai te shu de huan jing zao cheng le te shu de shi jian

qi zhong bao kuo ceng zai
nian du ling dong ji ao yun hui huo de

ye you gu cheng shi yi jian fei chang nan de er qie yi de shi qing

zhan shang qu dou bu gan wang xia kan
wo ma gen ben mei you tuo xie de yi si
wo zi ji xia lai le
he ma ma shuo
hai shi lian ba
ma ma jiu bao zhuo wo ku a
liu wei jian jian ke yi yong jiao zhi shi xian du li sheng huo
ta bu dan ke yi yong jiao jia zhuo bi xie zi
jia zhuo shao zi chi fan
hai ke yi yong jiao shu lian di chuan wa zi
fa shou ji duan xin
wan dian nao you xi
chai zhuang sai che mo xing
you qi na xie xi xiao de ling bu jian
shi liu wei de ai hao
zhe xie yong shou dou hen nan wan cheng de gong zuo
liu wei yong jiao zhi wan de chu qi de qing song
xie xie ni zhe me qi shi wo
hen duo shi hou
ming yun chang he ni kai wan xiao
ni yue xiang zuo shen me
ta yi ding hui gei ni zhi zao ma fan
ta jue ding xue xi you yong
bing jin le bei jing shi can ji ren you yong dui
zhi qian yi dian bu hui
zai jin xing shui shang kang fu xun lian shi
zi ji xia you
hui le na me yi dian
jin jin liang nian
liu wei jiu zai quan guo can ji ren you yong jin biao sai shang huo de le liang jin yi yin
hen duo ren jue de wo you yun dong tian fu
qi shi bu wan quan shi
wo xun lian de yuan yuan bi bie ren yao duo
liu wei dui mu qin xu xia nuo yan
nian de can ao hui shang na yi mei jin pai hui lai
jiu zai ta nu li bei zhan ao yun hui shi
gao qiang du de ti neng xiao hao dao zhi ta mian yi li xia jiang
huan shang le guo min xing zi dian
bi xu fang qi xun lian
fou ze jiang wei ji sheng ming
dang shi yi jing
sui de liu wei
gai he qu he cong
liu wei zi xi kao lv hou
zuo chu le yi ge rang quan jia ren dou qiang lie fan dui de jue ding
ta yong le zheng zheng yi ge yue de shi jian
chang shi shuo fu jia ren
di yi ge zhan chu lai zhi chi ta de hai shi ma ma
hui xiang qi dang chu de qing jing
liu wei hen gan ji
wo ma shi ge fei chang jie yue de ren
ta xiao shi hou sheng huo hen ku
cong wo chu shi zhi hou ta jiu bu shang ban le
zhi you fu qin yi ren zai gong zuo
dang shi mai qin yao hua
wan duo kuai qian
ta men ye you yu le hao jiu
ma ma wen wo hen duo bian
ni yi hou shi que ding yao tan ta ma
hai shi zhi you san tian re hu jin er
zui hou ta neng zhi chi wo
wo fei chang di gan dong
jie xia lai de wen ti shi xue xi
liu wei ceng jing zhao guo yi ge gang qin lao shi
wo zhi hui jiao ren yong shou tan qin
yong jiao wo zi ji ye bu hui
ta you zhao dao yi jia si li yin yue xue yuan
xiao zhang gei ta de hui ying shi
ni jin wo men xue xiao xue yin yue zhi neng shi ying xiang xiao rong

xie xie ni zhe me qi shi wo
wo hui rang ni kan kan wo shi zen me zuo de
ma ma bang zhuo ta
ba mai lai de gang qin jin xing gai zao
zai qin jian pang bian zuo le yi ge mu ji zuo
ke yi rang liu wei ba jiao gen dian zai shang mian jin xing tan zou
qin yi ye tiao zheng le gao du
cong er jie jue le shen ti zhong xin de wen ti
mei ren ke yi gao su liu wei gai zen yang yong jiao tan gang qin
kong zhi jiao zhi de ling huo du ye jue fei yi shi
kai shi jie zou dou zhang wo bu hao
zhe ge li du
ke neng tan yi ge yin
xia yi ge yin jiu mei sheng le
geng bie ti pei he le
lian dao hou lai jiao dou chou jin le ye bu de yao ling
jiao zhi tou bei mo po hen duo ci hou
liu wei jian jian mo suo chu jie chu qin jian de fang fa

jue de yong jiao tan bu ke neng

na shi bie ren yan li de

kai xue di yi ke
yao qing liu wei zuo jian chi meng xiang de biao yan jia bin

bian zuo zai gang qin pang yong yin yue lai biao da zi ji

zhe shi wo ting dao de zui mei di sheng yin
wo men neng yong de yi ge ci jiu shi zhen han

zai na yi ke shang

ke yi tian ma xing kong

jin nian jiu jin bang ti ming le
zai gao kao zhong
duo fen de hao cheng ji kao qu le tian jin shi fan da xue
bu jin shi ta men jia

ta bing mei you yin ci er gao xing

wei shen me yao man zhuo jia li ne

hai shi chu le shen me shi le ne
wei bang zhu da xue sheng mai bao chou xue fei

guo hai ping he bing ren jia shu yi yi gou tong guo
wu yi ren yuan yi yi zhen ming shi ren
geng bie shuo liang xiang
yi dan jin le jing shen bing yuan
jian hu quan jiu gui jia shu
bing ren zi ji mei quan li zuo jue ding
jia shu men de li you shi
ru guo ta men you yi tian chu yuan le
hui dao she hui shang hai yao jian ren
hai yao gong zuo
yao shi bei quan shi jie dou zhi dao de guo jing shen bing
jiu mei fa huo le
guo hai ping shuo
zhong guo pu tong min zhong dui jing shen bing ren ye huai zhuo ji da de kong huang he pai chi
guo hai ping she xiang guo zhe ge hua mian
bing ren men zhen de lai chu xi hua zhan le
da gai jiu lun dao xian chang guan zhong xia de hou tui san bu le
guo hai ping ye ceng gan dao kong ju
ta tuo zhuo yi zhi zhuang man shui cai yan liao
ma ke bi de xing li xiang zhu jin zu tang shan jing shen bing yuan de di yi ye
yi ge nv bing ren qi li de jiao han rang ta mao gu song ran
che ye wei mian
dan hen kuai ta bei ta men de hua zheng fu
mai hun tun chu shen de zhang yu bao
xi yong zui dui bi qiang lie de se cai
hua chu yi jie li bu cong xin de zhi tou
you xiang shi yi ge pao xiao de xiao ren
zhe fu zhang yu bao zi ji qu ming wei
de hua ling suo you ren di yi shi jian xiang dao le ai de hua
tong yang de niu qu
fen nu he tong ku
cong zhi mian shang ji hu pen bo er chu
ao man zi da de yu dan ge ge
yong tou shi fa hua qi che
bie shu he yi qie ta xiang xiang zhong di shang liu she hui
shen zhi ta hua de ao ba ma he guo hai ping dou wei miao wei xiao
yi bei zi lao shi ba jiao
yin wei zheng bu liao qian gei er zi gai fang qu xi fu er beng kui

jian chi hua you yong de dong xi
ta hua xian tiao ying lang
se cai xian yan de nong yong ji xie
hai you yi bei zi zhi zuo guo yi ci de huo che
suo you dou shi gao kong fu shi tu
zhe rang guo hai ping de chu jie lun

zhe xie bing ren dou hao wu hui hua ji chu

hao bu you yu

ta ke yi hua chu ta nao zi li de yi qie
wo wen yu dan ge ge ke bu ke yi hua yu
ta li ji hua le shi ji tiao yu
mei tiao dou you ming you xing

cha tai yuan le
wo men zai di shang
ta men zai tian shang
xian shi tai chen zhong le
suo yi ta men cai hun bu fu ti
ling hun chu qiao

guo hai ping zou de shi hou
zhang yu bao he wang jun dou ku le
guo hai ping da ying ta men
yao kai she yi ge yi shu bing qu
ji xu rang ta men hua hua
ta yi wei zhe bu shi yi jian nan shi
shen zhi hen kuai ye zheng qu dao liao jiang su fu cai zhong xin de yi bi zi zhu zi jin
dan yi yuan ju jue le ta de ti yi
yuan fang he jia shu dou dan xin
hua hua zhe yang de ci ji xing huo dong hui shi bing ren xing fen
er guo hai ping ti chu de wei le rang bing ren men bao chi jing li he ling gan er jian shao yao liang de yao qiu geng bei shi zuo bu ke xiang xiang
hua hua de shi hou ta men zhuan zhu
zai na duan ri zi li ta men de zhuang tai ming xian hao guo ping shi

ta fan kai le zu tang shan yi yuan qi bing qu zhu ren wang yu dang shi de zhi liao bi ji

ta de yi shu tian fu ling ren jing ya
zai san ge yue de shi jian li
ta mei tian dou zai chuang zuo

you gan yu zheng chang ren de biao da

jiu shi zhen dui zhe yang yi ge zheng ce de bian dong lai kao lv de
an guo qu de biao zhun
ci an pan jue que shi ming xian bu gong ping
cong si fa zheng ce de bian dong lai kan
yi fa zhan de yan guang lai kan
ta hai shi you yi ding de dao li de
zhong guo zheng fa da xue jiao shou ruan qi lin jie shou nan fang zhou mo ji zhe cai fang shi cheng
you bu fen xue zhe he lv shi dui yun nan sheng gao yuan de zuo fa chi zan tong yi jian
ren wei si xing fei chu ke cong ren he yi ge ge an zuo qi
ruan tong shi ren wei
ji bian you zheng ce bei jing de bian hua

shi zhi de tao lun de

fei chu si xing
zhe shi liang fa de li nian

ta ye shi fei chu si xing de zhi chi zhe
dan ta bu tong yi yun nan sheng gao yuan de zuo fa
jiu suan shi zhi xing yi zhong shao sha
shen sha de li nian er xuan ze yi ge an jian
ye bu neng xuan zhe yang yi ge an jian
ni xiang yin ling gong zhong

er qie ye ke yi tong guo si fa ji guan lai qi dong

zhe ge tuan huo shi qu nian
yue fen kai shi zai hang zhou zuo an de

zui hou dao liu ge zi cheng le qi zi zhang ting dui chen guang biao de ping jia
zai zhong guo xian jin ci shan shi ye zhong
chen guang biao de chu xian zhu ding shi ge ling lei
ta ceng biao shu
zai mou za zhi de cai fu pai hang bang shang
ta ming luo sun shan
ta geng duo shi yi yi zhong jin hu bao fa hu de mian kong deng chang
jian dan zhi jie ba huo zhen jia shi de zhen jin bai yin jiao dao bai xing shou zhong
duo ben rong yu zheng shu die jia zai yi qi
duo mian jin qi
duo tiao cang min song de ha da
zhe xie cheng le chen guang biao gong si zhan ting li de gui bao
nian chun jie qian xi
chen guang biao ba
wan xian jin dui cheng qian qiang shou fei yi
ying jiang di zhen
ta you yin wei yi zhang rang shou zhu zhe gao ju bai yuan da chao de zhao pian zai ci shou dao zhi ze
ta de gao diao xing shan you zhe tong nian de li shi gen yuan
chen guang biao sheng zai jiang su sheng si hong xian de nong cun jia ting
nian you de ta shi chang li yong zhong wu shi jian
dan shui qu ji zhen fan mai
yi nian shu jia
ta shi mai sui zhuan de
jiao wan zi ji de xue fei
ta hai bang ling yi wei jia jing pin han de tong xue jiao le shu ben fei
ban zhu ren wei ci gei ta ban fa yi ke xiao hong xing
ta yong kou shui ba xing xing tie zai lian shang
yi ci qu ge ban zhan shi
hong xing hou hua luo
ta yong bi ti chong xin tie shang
fang xue hou pao bian quan cun qu xuan yao
xiao hong xing zai ta you xiao xin ling mai xia de xin nian zhong zi ri yi cheng zhang
duo sui de chen guang biao hui xiang tong nian xiao hong xing de gu shi
xiao rong ke ju zhi tai sheng si hai tong
dang ni shou zhi zhi zhuo bie ren de shi hou
wen wen zi ji zuo le na xie shi

ta shuo ta xiang xin
gao diao ci shan zhe she

ta shen zhi chang chang zai ye jian xiao xing

chen guang biao gan kai
bao chi dan ding zhi xin

hao wu yi wen
chen guang biao de

hu nan sheng ci shan zong hui li shi
chang sha shi ci shan hui fu hui zhang
hu nan shi fan da xue li shi wen hua xue yuan jiao shou zhou qiu guang zhi chu

zai zhou qiu guang kan lai

ji yu xin yang
guo qing de ju da cha yi
zhong guo mu qian mei you tiao jian

fei zhuan ye xing de

ji zhe de cai fang

qi ye de kang feng xian neng li
qi ye jia de jia ting cheng yuan ji yuan gong xia gang de sheng huo bao zhang deng yi da dui she hui wen ti

zai hu nan wei shi
yue lu shi jian lun

yue shi wu yu heng liu de shi dai

que bao suo zi zhu xue sheng shi qiang shang jiang zhuang tie de man

dan cong ming fan bei cong ming wu

chang chang shi ta yi kai kou
da jia jiu xiao
ta yong lao jia de hua wen yi ju ni mai ma
ni mai shen me
na ge hen hen de ma ye hui rang bie ren wu yi wei ta zai ma ren
yi jia ren di yi ci qu tian an men shi
zai mo sheng de cheng li dao chu wen lu
ke lu ren si hu dou bu neng li jie ta men de yi si
ba ma zui hou zhi neng peng zhuo bei jing di tu
ping shou shi gao su bie ren ta men yao qu de di fang
na shi hou gen sheng ren shuo hua te bie niu
gao jun qi xiao zhuo dui wo hui yi dao
zai bei jing sheng huo le zhe xie nian
ta de xiang yin yi jing xiao shi
shuo de yi kou chun zheng de pu tong hua
ou er tiao pi di mo fang yi ju da ye
nin chi guo le ma
hai jing wei shi zu
xiao nan hai an di li xia gong fu
ta zong shi liu xin ting cun zi li de ben di hai zi shuo hua
ba bie ren de fa yin ji zai xin li
ti xing zi ji
xia ci kai kou yi ding ye yao zhe me shuo
ke you xie shi hou
ta yi zhang zui you dai shang le xiang yin
xin li jiu te bie gan ga
zai xue xiao li
ta yin yin gan jue ping zhuo zi ji de kou yin
huo zhe zi ji de chuan zhuo
bie de xiao peng you qing yi jiu cha jue chu zi ji de bu yi yang
zhe suo gong ban xue xiao li ji hu mei you qi ta wai di hai zi
gao jun qi zong gan jue yu bie ren you ju li
ni bie fu qiang a
fu qiang rang ni ba ma lai shua qi
yi ci ke jian
ta zhan bu wen fu le yi xia qiang
yi ge tong xue ma shang zhe yang jing gao ta
zhe you ti xing le ta de bu yi yang
ba ba dang ban yun gong
ma ma dang bao jie yuan
er qi ta tong xue de ba ma ke yi zai da shang chang li gong zuo
huo zhe ping zhuo zi jia fang chan lai shou zu
ta hai xi xin di liu yi dao
yu zi ji jia zu zhu de shui jiao
zuo fan dou zai yi kuai er de xiao ping fang bu yi yang
xu duo ben di hai zi dou zhu zai liang ceng xiao lou li
jia li wo shi
chu fang fen de te bie qing
gao jun qi yi tian zui kuai huo de shi guang
shi xia ke hou pao hui cun li
yu san wu ge tong yang lai zi wai di de hai zi feng wan
pai pu ke pai
ta men jie shou le zi ji yu ben di hai zi de bu yi yang
zi jue di xing cheng zi ji de quan zi
bu gen ta men wan
wo xue hui le zi ji gei zi ji jiang xiao hua
gao jun qi zai zhe suo gong ban xiao xue li zhi shang le yi zhou de ke
zai zhe ge cun zi li ye zhi dai le shi ji tian
ba ma gen zhe xiang shu de lao xiang
ban dao liao wei yu chao yang qu de xian ning hou cun
bi qi tong zhou lai
zhe li li tian an men geng jin le xie
fan zheng na li dou you xue xiao ma
jun qi ma ma xin li xiang
ke zai mo sheng de xian ning hou cun
gao jia de xin fang dong yu zhe li gong ban xiao xue de xiao zhang shuo bu shang hua er
yao ru xue de jiao liang san qian yuan de fei yong
fu fu liang dang shi yi ge yue de shou ru hai bu dao
suo yi ma shang da xiao le jin gong ban de nian tou
ba mu guang zhuan xiang le min ban xue xiao
na er yi xue qi xue fei si wu bai kuai
fan fei ye pian yi
ta men hai dao cun li tou jie hai zi
shang wan ke zai song hui lai
jun qi ma ma hai ji de
na shi mei dao kai xue qian
xu duo min ban xue xiao jiu zai cun li long ge zhuo zi zhao sheng
ta zui zhong wei er zi xuan ding le li jia
fen zhong che cheng de jing hua xi wang xue xiao
zai zhe ge xin xue xiao li
er nian ji hai mei du wan de gao jun qi cheng le san nian ji de cha ban sheng
zhe li de jiao shi
qiang shang lao diao qi
mei ge xiao peng you ye you yi tao zhuo yi
ke mu zhuo zi shang jin shi xiao dong
mu yi zi yi zuo jiu huang you
fang ding shi wa pian da de
wai mian xia da yu li mian ye xia xiao yu
yi qun xiao peng you zhe shi bian na er bu lou wang na er ji yi dian
dan ta que gan jue
xin jiao shi geng zi zai
tong xue men dou shi wai di lai de hai zi
shuo zhuo wu hu si hai de fang yan
tong yang shuo bu hao de shi ying yu
ta jiu zhao dao yi ge si dang
xiao pang zi shi he bei ren
gen zhe zuo juan lian men de ba ma lai dao bei jing
ta kou cai hao
ke jian zui ai gei da jia shuo xiao hua
yi qun tong xue chang chang bei dou de qian yang hou he
ke si nian ji de chun jie gang guo
xiao pang zi tu ran bu lai shang ke le
gao jun qi si chu da ting
cai zhi dao ta yi jing gen zhe ba ma ban zou le
gao jun qi zi ji li kai tong zhou de cun zi shi
ye gen xiao pang zi yi yang
shi xian hao bu zhi qing
hou lai ta gen zhe ba ma fan hui tong zhou shou shi yu xia de jia dang
yi xin pan zhuo hai neng jian dao yuan lai de san wu ge huo ban
mei xiang dao na xie hai zi ye yi jing xiang zi ji yi yang
gen zhe fu mu piao dao liao bie chu
gao jun qi ji bu qing you yu fang dong jia zu huo shou hui fang zi er ban le duo shao ci jia
xing yun de shi
ta men yi jia zai ye mei li kai xian ning hou cun
ta ye wu xu xiang qi ta da gong zi di na yang
pin fan di geng huan xue xiao
ke zai ta yi zhi jiu du de xue xiao li
fen li que cong wei jian duan
mei ge chun jie guo hou
ban shang dou you da gai san fen zhi yi de tong xue li kai

ke shi ji shang
da an bing bu you zhe xie hai zi lai jue ding
chun jie qi jian
ta men de fu mu hui lao jia hou chang chang you le xin de da gong ji hua
lai nian bian dai shang ta men yi ju bie chu
ta men dou bu zhi dao zi ji hui li kai
gao jun qi dui wo shuo zhuo
yu diao man le xia lai
yan jing yi zhi kan zhuo yuan fang
jiu pa kai xue shi jian bu dao yuan lai de peng you
bu jin shi xue sheng
lao shi ye bu duan lai lai wang wang
gao jun qi ji de
cong xiao xue san nian ji dao chu zhong san nian ji
ta yi gong huan le
ci ban zhu ren
lao shi yi huan
gan jue na ke tang jiu mo sheng le
jiang ke de fang shi bu yi yang
tou ji jie ke hen duo ren ting bu dong
lao shi jiu wen wo men zen me jiang ke cai neng ting dong
gan jue gu dan de shi hou
ta jiu chen fu mu da dian hua hui lao jia shi
yu tang di liao ji ju
lai tian an men wan ba
ta zong shi zhe yang dui tang di shuo
yi zhi zai lao jia nian shu de tang di tong guo wang luo kan guo xu duo tian an men de zhao pian
que yi zhi mei you dao guo bei jing
wo zou le zhi hou
ta ren shi le hao duo hao peng you
xian zai hai xiang yi qian na me kuai le
gao jun qi de yu diao bian de geng man le
wo yi shi bu zhi dao gai shuo shen me
ta shen bian gu ding de peng you liao liao wu ji
yu ta yi lu tong chuang de
zhi you yi ge nan hai

yue zhong xun bi ye hou
tong xue men si san li kai

gang yi kai kou

zai bu hui qu
wo jiu qian tu miao mang le
gao jun qi liu nian ji de shi hou

gai zhi wei yi suo min ban gong zhu de gong yi xue xiao

shen me shi xin gong min
gao jun qi zhi jin ji de

ben di ren le

ta men bu neng zai bei jing sheng du gao zhong he can jia gao kao
lao shi hai shuo
kao lv dao bei jing he wai di zai jiao cai ji jiao yu shui ping shang de cha yi

ta hai mei lai de ji zi xi si kao

bu jin ai wan hai ai yan jiu de shao nian zhi shi mo mo hu hu di huan xiang guo

jiu shi you yi ci juan ru jia fa piao shi jian zhong

ta cong xia jin xian mei shu pin chang ci zhi hou

zhao yu xin si chu san fa ce zi

you qi hui gao xing wei yi shu

yu men zhi yu

ren e ji le jiu da qi le da dui cang ku li liang shi de zhu yi
er zuo wei cang ku bao guan yuan de zhong mei sheng
zi ran jiu yin qi le zhe xie ren de guan zhu
sheng chan dui chang he yi ge she yuan tu ran zhao dao le zhong mei sheng
shuo jie dao shang ji ming ling
yao zhuan yi yi bu fen liang shi
na ge shi hou shi xing yi yuan hua ling dao
dui zhang shuo shen me jiu shi shen me
bu ting hua shi yao bei pi dou de
dang tian wan shang san ge ren jiu ba jiang jin
jin de liang shi zhuan yi dao liao qi ta di fang
zhi yu zhe xie liang shi hou lai qu le na li
zhong mei sheng yi dian ye bu zhi dao
ye mei you da ting
ge yue zhi hou
que fa sheng le yi jian da shi
da dui yao wang zhen shang jiao gong liang
jiu zai song gong liang de lu shang you ren lai qiang liang shi
gong she shi hou diao cha
hu she yuan li yong song liang shi de shi ji qiang zou le
zhe zai dang shi ke shi yi jian le bu de de da shi
gong she pai ren diao cha
hen kuai jiu zhao dao le zhi qian bei dui zhang he zhong mei sheng zhuan yi zou de na xie liang shi
diao cha ren yuan ren wei
shi zhong mei sheng jian shou zi dao
ke zhong mei sheng shuo ta zhi shi zhi xing sheng chan dui chang de ming ling
mei you tou liang shi
zai shang ge shi ji liu shi nian dai
tou liang shi shi zhong zui
zai zhe jian shi shang
zhi you zhong mei sheng hou lai bei ding le ji ti tou liang zui
nian you qi tu xing
ling wai liang ge ren dou mei you shou dao chu fa
an zhao zhong mei sheng de shuo fa
dang nian shi san ge ren zuo le zhe jian shi
na wei xing li de she yuan yi jing qu shi le
de ji zhe zhao dao liao dang nian de sheng chan dui chang leng mou
leng mou hui da
dang nian de shi qing yi jing bu ji de le
zhong mei sheng shuo
yin wei you ren bao hu sheng chan dui chang he ling wai yi ge she yuan
suo yi ta men dou mei you shou dao chu fa
zhi you zi ji
bi jing chu le zhe me da de shi
ken ding yao you ren cheng dan ze ren de
ke zhong mei sheng zen me ye mei you xiang dao
zi ji hui wei ci zuo le
er zhe dou shi yin wei ta qi zi de yi ju hua
dou shi lao po re de huo
sui jiu jie hun le
qi zi shi lin cun de yi ge nv hai
jia guo lai bu jiu
jiu dang shang le cun li de fu nv zhu ren
zhong mei sheng shuo
jie hun zhi hou
ta he qi zi de guan xi yi zhi bu shi hen hao
hou lai jiu you ren gao su ta
qi zi he sheng chan dui li de yi ge ren hao shang le
ta yi zhi ye mei zai yi
zhong lao han shuo
zai tou liang zhe jian shi shang
zheng fa bu zhang zhao guo ta de qi zi
wen pan duo chang shi jian he shi
ta de qi zi jiu shuo le yi ju
sui ran hen duo lin ju ye zheng shi
zhong mei sheng suo shuo de dou shi shi hua
ke wo men hen nan xiang xiang yi ge nv ren hui zhe me dui dai zi ji de zhang fu
zhong mei sheng shuo
ta ru yu zhi hou
qi zi jiu he ta li hun le
hou lai liang ge ren zai ye mei jian guo
de ji zhe zhan zhuan zhao dao le ta
zhong mei sheng de qian qi bu cheng ren zi ji dang chu shuo guo na me yi ju hua
ta shuo zhong mei sheng ru yu hou
zi ji gai jia le
he zhong jia zai ye mei you ren he lian xi
shang ge shi ji liu shi nian dai
fa lv bu wan shan
er qie dang shi de si fa shen pan ye bu du li
hen duo an zi dou shi dang wei
zheng fu he fa yuan yi qi shang liang ding zui de
ke bu guan zen me shuo
wei le bu dao
jin de liang shi
jiu pan zhong mei sheng
zhe ge xing fa guo zhong le
zhong mei sheng shuo
zhe zhong jian hai you bie de yuan yin
zheng fa bu zhang ceng jing gen zhong lao han shuo
tou liang shi zhe jian shi yong bu liao pan shi nian
yao xiang pan shi nian ke yi gai cheng fen
ba cheng fen gai cheng di zhu
jiu ke yi pan
zheng ge she hui hai chu yu jie ji dou zheng de shi dai
zai zhe yang yi ge te shu de bei jing xia
yi ge ren de chu shen jiu cheng le yi ge fei chang guan jian de yin su
xian zai yao xiang pan zhong xing
ye zhi neng cong cheng fen shang xiang ban fa
zhong mei sheng jiu de dao xiao xi
ta fu qin de cheng fen bei gai cheng lou wang de di zhu fen zi
er ta zi ran cheng le di zhu zi di
an zi de xing zhi ma shang jiu bian le
yuan ben de ren min nei bu mao dun
bian cheng le jie ji dou zheng
jiu zhe yang zhong mei sheng bei pan le
zhong mei sheng bei song dao liao fu jin de li xian nong chang
jin xing lao dong gai zao
zhong mei sheng jiu you shang su de xiang fa
ke ta dang shi que bu gan zhe yang zuo
shen su wu guo
dang shi you hen duo gen zhong lao han yi yang you yuan qing de ren

zhong lao han jiu ren le xia lai
yi ge fen dui chang zhi dao le ta de shi

gu li ta xie shen su cai liao
ta cai kai shi xie

ta jiu pan zhuo zao yi tian chu qu

zhong mei sheng duo ci li gong

qi zi bi ta da

wen ge jie shu

yu shi ta xie le chu yu yi hou de di yi fen shen su cai liao
ke da ji sui zhi er lai
gong she jiang da dui li fen gei zhong jia de shu dou shou zou le
hou lai hai chai le zhong jia de yi jian fang zi
zhe ge zhong bu gong ping de dai yu

zui kun nan de shi hou

de le jing shen bing
zhong mei sheng de mei mei

hou lai he nong yao zi sha
xing hao bei ren jiu le hui lai

zhe cheng le zhong mei sheng de yi kuai xin bing
ta wu shi wu ke bu xiang zheng ming zi ji de qing bai
bai tuo zhe ge shen fen
jie dao zhong mei sheng de shen su cai liao hou
yuan yuan jiang xian ping fan gong zuo zu ceng jing zhao guo ta

bu shi ren ming guan tian de shi qing
wo jue de ke yi yi hou zai chu li
wo jue dui bu hui yin wei zhe ge xiao shi
ting zhi wo de pei xun
jue dui bu hui
jia bao shi jian zheng zheng yi zhou zhi hou
mei ti de bao dao yi jing bu ke neng zai hu shi shi
li yang hui dao bei jing
zai pai chu suo he
da cheng xie yi
bao zheng bu zai shi shi bao li
gong kai dao qian
bing jie shou xin li zi xun shi de zhuan ye bang zhu
li yang dui mei ti tan cheng
ta men fu qi zhi jian de chong tu yi jing chi xu le duo nian
er qie bao li ye zai bu duan di sheng ji
hui shi sheng ji de guo cheng
ni shi yi ge zai mei guo zhang da de nv hai
ni wei shen me hui ren shou le zhe me chang shi jian ne
wo men hao de shi hou zhen de fei chang hao
wei ci wo neng ren shou huai de shi hou
dan zhe ci wo bu neng zai ren
wo dan xin wo he ta zai yi qi yi jing shang hai dao wo de nv er men
wo bu neng zai deng geng jiu
shi bao de nei zai yuan yin jiao yu shi ye he jia ting ze ren
li yang zai jie shou cai fang shi shuo guo
ta men de chong tu shi zhi shi yin wei ta gong kai zai mei ti shang biao da bu ai qi zi
bu zhu zhong jia ting
zui bu neng ren shou de shi ni dui wai shuo ni bu ai ta
dang shi shuo wo gen ta zai yi qi shi wei le zuo jia ting jiao yu de shi yan
ni shuo cheng li zhe ge jia ting shi wei le zhong mei jiao yu de zhe ge shi yan
na xiao hai hui jue de
wo zhi shi yi ge shi yan pin
you hao de shi yan pin he bu hao de shi yan pin a
ru guo wo men ba ta shi yan de hen hao
na shi yi ge sheng ming a
sheng ming ye shi yi ge shi yan pin a
xiao bai shu bu shi na lai shi yan de ma
dan shi ta men zui da de cai
ta ting dao zhe ge shuo fa zhi hou zhi shi jue de shuo
yuan lai wo ba ba zhi shi hen gong li de mu di cai yao le wo
ying gai shuo wo ba ba wei le zhong guo jia ting jiao yu de shi ye yao le wo men
ye ke yi huan ge jiao du chu fa
zhe me duo nian
ni zui jie yi de jiu shi ta shuo de zhe ju hua
wo zhen de bu yao ting
xiao hai ting le yi hou
ta men gan jue shen me yi si
wo ma wo ba mei you ai
ken ding shi bu xing de
wo zhi dao ta hen xi huan feng kuang de
feng kuang shi feng kuang
ren shi you gan jue de
mei ji jiao shi
lai dao zhong guo
li yang hen xin shang ta de ying yu jiao xue fang fa
pin qing ta dan ren mei ji zong bian ji
ji nian hou ta men jie hun bing sheng le san ge nv er
shuo li yang yu ta ren shi shi you yu gong tong de ying yu jiao yu meng xiang
dan bing fei mei you wen qing
ni shuo yi ge cheng yu
hua long dian jing
qi si wo le
wei shen me wo ai ta
wo jue de ta de xin shi lao shi de xin
yao gai bian zhong guo de wei lai
nian de shi hou
mei tian wo men yi qi
yi qi gong zuo
wo men zi ji xie
hai you yi qi lu yin de
hao duo de xue sheng shuo
wo ting ni men de lu yin le
neng ting dao ni men wei xiao de gan jue
wo men dou lian hong le
dan hun hou li yang wei yi biao da ai yi de fang shi
jin jin shi zan mei
shi ge wei da de mu qin he jiao yu jia
ta ceng jing zai jie hun shi yi zhou nian de na tian
de ti xing xia
fa guo yi tiao gan xie de wei bo
dan shi hou cai zhi dao ta bing bu gao xing
hao duo ci ta shuo wo shi hen hao de ma ma
ke shi bang de ma ma
ken ding wo shi ge ma ma
dan wo hai shi nv sheng de
wo shi ta tai tai
wo mei ting guo ta shuo wei shen me ai wo
jiu shi shuo ji ran dou zai yi qi le
hai ai shen me ai
ai gai dou gua zai zui bian
yin wei ni zhi ba ta dang zuo yi ge ma ma
er ta hai you yi ge hen zhong yao de shen fen
ta shi ni de qi zi
ta shi yi ge nv ren
ni ba ta de zhe yi bu fen zi wo
ru guo wu shi ta de cun zai
zhi ba ta dang cheng yi ge ma ma
ta hui jue de bu bei ren ke
suo yi you qiang hua liao dang nian wo na yi ju hua
wo gen ta zai yi qi wei le shi zuo jia ting jiao yu de shi ye
you yu li yang de gong si zong bu zai guang zhou
jia shang chang nian zai wai yan jiang
ta mei ge yue zhi you yi liang tian de shi jian dai zai bei jing
ta shen zhi bu zhi dao qi zi nv er de sheng ri
zai wei bo zhong shuo zi ji shi yi ge zhun dan qin ma ma
mei ge yue yi tian hui lai
liang tian hui lai
wo jue de zai gong si da sao de a yi
mei ge yue peng dao ta yi tian liang tian
gen wo cha bu duo
ni wei zhe ge jia ting fu chu shen me le
wo fu chu hen duo
ni neng bu neng gen wo shuo yi xia
ni ren wei zui rang ni zui gan dong de shi qing shi shen me
ke yi yi tian dou bu hui jia
mei nian hai neng
lao da xue xiao de biao yan
ta mei hui lai
wo ting ta peng you shuo
li li ni ba ba ne
wo lao da shuo
ta hen mang de
wo hui shuo ying yu
wo bu xu yao wo ba ba de bang zhu
bie de xiao hai xu yao wo ba ba
li yang feng kuang jiao ying yu duan luo
tan shuai di shuo
yao geng zi si
zai jia ting dang zhong
ying gai shi zhe yang
yin wei wo ke neng hui geng duo de qu man zu wo shi ye shang de xu yao
dai gei wo de yi xie cheng jiu gan
zhang fu de zhe ge zhuang tai
ji wei wu nai
ta chang qi zai zhong guo sheng huo
jia zhao he jiao shi zhi zhao dou yi jing guo qi
sheng huo zhong di kun nan he gu du
rang ta yue lai yue xi wang li yang neng geng duo di hui gui jia ting
zhe zhong mao dun ji yuan ri shen
suo yi ni men lia zhe ci chong tu jiu jing shi zhi shi shen me
wo shuo dao tou lai shi que shi
que shi ta xian zai de ya li
jiu shi wo mei you xiang ta na yang qu gan shou ta de ya li
wo kan li yang shuo le yi ju hua
ru guo ni zai wen rou yi xie
ran hou wu suo wei yi dian
ken ding ni men lia guan xi hui geng hao yi xie
ni shuo hen mang de
mei hui lai de
wo ken ding pi qi bi jiao gao
wo men bi ci hen shan yu ji nu dui fang
yi jing bian cheng yi zhong you xi le
yi ge ren qi shi zui bei can de jiu shi
wan quan bei qing xu kong zhi
ni ken ding bu hui yong zhe yang de fang shi qu dui dai yi ge mo sheng ren
da jie shang de nv xing
na dang ran de
da jie shang de nv xing wo mei you li you zhe yang dui ta
fu qi zhi jian shi hen shao kong zhi zi ji
ren ba zui hao de yi mian dou liu gei le bie ren
xiang guan bao dao
li yang wei bo shang xiang qi zi dao qian mi shu cheng shuang fang yi he hao
li yang mei ji qi zi pi lu geng duo jia bao xi jie cheng yao li hun
can ji nan zi shou yang chun e lie qi ying huo jiu zhu wei yang nv zhi hao bing
xiao rong zhen zheng zhan fang zai
sui de zheng wen yan lian shang
na shi wan zheng de xiao rong
qu san le chun e lie de yin ying
zhe zhong xian tian xing yi chuan bing ji hu zai yi kai shi jiu cui hui le ta de ming yun
ta bei qin sheng fu mu yi qi zai chan fang men kou
dan zheng shi zai zhe li
ta he ling yi ge yin ji bing er can que de sheng ming xiang yu
yi ge ming jiao zheng bao zhong de zhong nian nan ren ba ta jian hui jia li
fu yang zhi jin
ta yin wei tui bu can ji wu fa zhan li
zhi neng kao pa xing qian jin
shou shu cheng gong
dang xiao wen yan dui zhuo shou li de xiao jing zi yi ci you yi ci zhan kai xiao rong shi
zheng bao zhong quan zai bing fang de yi jiao
an jing di xiao zhuo
ta zi ji de tui yi wu kang fu de ji hui
wo zhen gao xing
yan er zhong yu zhi hao le
zhe ge lai zi he bei ding xing de nan ren shuo
fang fu zhe yi jing dai gei ta ren sheng zhong zu gou de xin wei
yi ge ceng jing bu gan xiao de nv hai
yi ge zhi jin wu fa zhan li de nan ren
ta men de sheng ming yin wei bi ci bian de wan zheng qi lai
jiu xiang zhe ge nian ji de da duo shu nv hai yi yang
xiao wen yan xi huan yi qie mei li de dong xi
ta chuan zhuo fen hong se de qun zi
yong xian yan de hong se tu mo zi ji xiao xiao de shou zhi jia
shi bu shi de
ta hai hui dui zhuo yi mian fen hong se de xiao jing zi
you dian xiu se di lie kai zui
kan kan zi ji de mian pang
ta yi jing ke yi fang xin di qu xiao le
chun e lie ceng shi ta de shang chun he ya chuang cong bi gen fen lie cheng liang ban
yi xiao qi lai
jiu hui lu chu li mian ji ke bai bai de ya chi
yin wei zhe ge huo kou
ta cong bu gan zhang zui da xiao
hen duo shi hou lian wei xiao ye hui wu zhu zui
yin wei jue de zi ji he bie ren bu yi yang
ta xiao qi lai bu zai gu ji
ta ai gen zheng bao zhong shuo hua
ye ai zhan zai ta shen hou
shen chu shuang bi
fu shen bao zhu ta de bo zi
ping chang zai jia li
wen yan dui zheng bao zhong de cheng hu bu shi ba ba
er shi da bo
zhe shi zheng bao zhong zi ji de yi si
ru guo guan wo jiao ba ba
guan shui jiao ma ma ne
wo pa dui yan er de ying xiang bu hao
xiao wen yan ya ya xue yu shi zui zao hui shuo de ci
bu shi ba ba
er shi da bo
sui de da bo he
sui de yang nv zhan zai yi qi shi
zheng bao zhong de gao du zhi neng da dao xiao wen yan de xiong kou
ta cong lai mei you zhan qi lai guo
zhi neng dian zhuo jiao dun zhuo
yi shou cheng zhao di mian
yi shou wo zhuo zi ji can ji de you tui
yin wei tong nian de yi chang yi liao shi gu
zheng bao zhong de you tui ting liu zai ying er shi de cu xi
wu fa cheng shou ren he zhong liang
zai pang ren kan qi lai
ta xing zou de yang zi geng xiang pa
you hei gan shou de zuo shou zhua zhuo yi kuai zhuan tou da xiao de mu kuai
yu zuo tui jiao ti zhuo xiang qian mai chu
you shou ze wo zhuo you tui xi xi de jiao huai
ban zhuo ta yi dian yi dian qian jin
ta jiu zhe yang pa zhuo
ling zhuo xiao wen yan zai bei jing wan cheng le qian hou liang ci chun e lie de xiu fu shou shu
yi sheng men xian jiang wen yan liang pian lie kai de zui chun zi xi feng he qi lai
di er ci shou shu zhong ze cong ta de gu pen qu xia yi kuai ruan gu
bu dao ya yin de que kou li
jiu xiang yong shi zi tian ping di mian di xiao keng
shou shu wan cheng hou
zheng bao zhong dai zhuo wen yan zuo chang tu qi che hui dao zi ji wei yu he bei ding xing tian bian cun de jia li
jie fang lin ju men ting shuo xiao xi dou pao guo lai
zheng zhuo yao kan bian piao liang de zheng jia gui nv
zhe shi yan er de ming hao
zheng bao zhong zuo zai jia li po jiu de yi zi shang shuo
chuang wai de yuan zi li
wen yan zheng zai he biao mei zhui zhu da nao
na shi ta yong yuan ye wu fa zuo dao de shi qing
yin wei shen ti de can ji
zheng bao zhong shi qu le zu cheng jia ting de ji hui
ta yi zhi you shou yang yi ge hai zi de yuan wang
ta de da shen du gui rong zai xian yi yuan kan bing shi
zai fu chan ke de lou dao li kan dao yi wei lao ren bao zhuo hai zi
zhan zai chan fang men kou
du gui rong cou guo qu dou le liang xia
zhe shi ni jia hai zi ma
dui fang yao le yao tou
zhe hai zi da gai shi bei qin sheng fu mu yi qi le
du gui rong ren bu zhu ba zhe ge an jing tang zai yi juan bai se bei zi li de xiao ying er jie guo lai
bao zai zi ji huai li
ta kan bu chu zhe ge gang chu sheng mei liang tian de hai zi de yang mao
hai zi lie cheng liang ban de xiao zui chun
ta kan le ji yan cai fen bian chu lai
ye xu yin wei zhe yang
fu mu cai bu yao ta le ba
du gui rong xiang zhuo
tan le kou qi
ta jie zhe xiang dao le yi zhi xiang shou yang hai zi de zhi zi zheng bao zhong
ta da tong le zhi zi de dian hua
mei guo duo jiu
zheng bao zhong jiu da zhuo cun li lin ju de mo tuo che cong cong gan le guo lai
zhe shi zhe dui fu nv de di yi ci xiang yu
dang zheng bao zhong kan jian du gui rong huai li bao zhuo de nv ying shi
ji ji di pa guo qu
xiang shen shou jie guo lai bao bao
ke you tui de can ji rang ta zheng ge shen ti dou bi xu yi kao shuang shou de zhi cheng
gen ben mei fa qu bao
ta zhi neng quan zai du gui rong de shen pang
nu li shen zhuo bo zi
zi xi di kan le kan na zhang you que xian de xiao lian
nian zhi hou de jin tian
dang you ren fan fu zhui wen
dao di shi shen me rang ta jue ding shou yang zhe ge xian tian can ji de nv hai shi
zhe ge lao shi de nan ren zhi shi bu ting di shuo

wo dang shi zhi dan xin

zheng bao zhong shuo
zhe shi ge ren
shi ge xing ming a
ta he du gui rong yi qi ba hai zi bao hui le jia
yu ta tong zhu de fu qin zheng wan liang gei hai zi qi le ge hao ting de ming zi
zhe shi wo men zheng jia wen zi bei de hai zi
er qie shi yi zhi
fei lai de yan er
zheng wan liang xiao zhuo shuo
zhi yu rang xiao wen yan zao dao yi qi de huo zui
zheng bao zhong bing mei you fang zai xin shang
ta zhi shi qing miao dan xie di yao yao tou
dou bao hui lai le
shui hai zai hu zhe ge
sui zhe zhe zhi fei lai de yan er de dao lai
zheng bao zhong de dan shen han sheng huo li ke bu yi yang le
ta kai shi ben zhuo di xue zhuo zhao gu xiao wen yan
ta dou yong kai shui chong hao nai fen
yong xiao shao yao qi yi dian
zi ji shi shi wen du
zai man man song dao hai zi zui li
du gui rong ji de
zi ji zou dao zheng bao zhong jia
fa xian fu zi liang ren zheng shou mang jiao luan di hong zhuo qiang bao zhong bu duan ti ku de ying er
zao zhi dao bu bao hui lai
ye bu gei ni men zeng jia fu dan le
du gui rong ban kai wan xiao di shuo
zheng bao zhong mei you hui da
ta zhi shi yi bian hong zhuo kang shang xiao xiao de wen yan
yi bian wei wei di xiao zhuo
zai xiao wen yan bei bao hui lai yi ge yue zhi hou
zheng bao zhong ba quan jia ren jiao zai yi qi
an zhao dang di de xi su
gei zi ji zhe ge gui nv guo le ge re nao de man yue li
cong na zhi hou
zheng jia du hui xia yi wan chang shou mian
wei zhe zhi fei lai de yan er
guo yi ge tui suan chu lai de
bing bu que qie de sheng ri

wu lun zou dao na li
jia li de yan er dou shi zhe ge nan ren zui chang dian ji de xin shi
ke ta bing bu jue de zi ji neng gei hai zi de ming yun dai lai shen me da de zhuan bian
zhe ge zai nong cun zhang da de nan ren gen ben mei shen me yuan da de mu biao
ta wei yi de yuan wang
jiu shi ba xiao wen yan yang huo
er qie neng pao neng tiao neng dian
bu yao xiang zi ji zhe yang
dan gai bian jiu zhe me lai le
zheng bao zhong zai xian cheng de yi ge gong chang li da ling gong
wu xiu de shi hou
ta mei shen me shi zuo
jiu pa dao xian cheng zui da de ding xing guang chang
ta fa xian le yi tiao hong se de tiao fu
yi qun gong zuo ren yuan zhan zai pang bian
hao zhao da jia gei pin kun shi xue er tong juan kuan
neng bang bie ren jiu bang yi dian bei
ta zhe yang xiang zhuo
jiu le he he di cou le guo qu
mo le mo kou dai
fa xian zi ji hai sheng xia yi kuai wu mao qian
yi kuai qian yao liu gei yan er mai shao bing
ta zhuo mo zhuo
zhun bei ba sheng xia de wu mao qian juan chu qu
dan zou dao juan kuan xiang pang bian
ta you you xie bu hao yi si le
zhe me dian er qian
neng bang shang bie ren ma
lai hui zhuan le hao ji quan
zheng bao zhong hai shi xia ding jue xin
pa dao juan kuan xiang qian
shen chang le ge bo
ba wu mao qian sai le jin qu
zhe fu hua mian xi yin le yi wei gong zuo ren yuan de zhu yi
dang ta zhun bei li kai de shi hou
zhe wei gong zuo ren yuan lan zhu le ta
gei wo men qian ge ming ba
zheng bao zhong zhe cai fa xian
zhuo zi qian gua zhuo de heng fu shang
yi jing xie man le juan kuan ren de ming zi
ta yao yao tou
jue de te bie bu hao yi si
ke jin bu zhu dui fang de fan fu yang qiu
ta hai shi jie guo bi
dun zai di shang
zai heng fu shang wai wai niu niu di xie xia le zi ji de ming zi
zhe ge mei shang guo xue de nan ren ye bu hui xie bie de shen me zi le
gong chang de lao ban zhao dao le ta
wen ta shi bu shi can jia guo shen me juan kuan
wo jiu juan le yi dian
zheng bao zhong shuo
xiang dao zi ji zhi juan le wu mao qian
ta jiu jue de hun shen bu de jin
dan dang di dian shi tai zai bao dao zhe ci juan kuan shi zhu yi dao liao ta
xi wang dao ta jia li qu zuo yi ge cai fang
dang tian xia wu
zai cun li po jiu de fang nei
zheng bao zhong ke ke ba ba di jiang shu le zi ji juan kuan de jing guo
ji zhe ye zhi dao le ta shou yang xiao wen yan de shi
can ji yang fu shou yang chun lie yang nv de gu shi hen kuai zai ding xing xian chuan kai le
mei guo duo jiu
ding xing xian can lian de gong zuo ren yuan ye lai dao le zheng bao zhong de jia li
ta men bang ta chong xin fen shua fang jian de qiang bi
ye bu shang le yuan ben lou yu de wu ding
xian zhang shen zhi te pi le lv se tong dao
rang zheng bao zhong gan jin bu ban shou yang wen yan de shou xu
zheng bao zhong zhe cai zhi dao
shou yang hai zi bu zhi shi bao hui lai na me jian dan
yang ge hai zi hai yao ban shou xu
wo dang shi sha ye bu zhi dao
ta hui yi shuo
zai ban li shou yang shou xu zhi qian
an zhao gui ding
zheng bao zhong zai dang di de fa zhi bao shang deng le
qi xun ren qi shi
xun zhao xiao wen yan de qin sheng fu mu
zhe rang zheng bao zhong zong jue de you dian jin zhang
ta hai pa wen yan de fu mu tu ran chu xian
hai pa zi jia fei lai de yan er you tu ran di fei zou le
zhe hai zi ben lai jiu shi ta men bu yao
wo men cai guang ming zheng da di jian lai de
ta you xie mei tou mei nao di an wei zi ji
wen yan de fu mu mei you zhao lai
zheng bao zhong cai zhong yu song le kou qi
zai bao hui wen yan liang tian zhi hou
zheng bao zhong ceng jing he da shen hui dao yi yuan
zhuan men da ting guo wen yan fu mu de qing kuang
ta men tong guo hu shi zhao dao le wen yan qin sheng mu qin de chuang wei
pang bian de ren gao su ta men
zhe wei mu qin gang gang sheng le yi dui long feng tai
yin wei nv er you can ji
suo yi liang tian qian song gei bie ren le
na ge shi hou
zheng bao zhong tou tou di kan le yi yan na dui fu mu
fa xian dui fang dou shi da gao ge er
zhang de ye hao
ta chang cai ce
jiu yin wei zhe yang
zai cun zi li
wen yan ye zong bei lin ju men kua zan zhang de piao liang
huan ying fa biao ping lun wo yao ping lun
nan zi shen bei pen qi dong li yi fei yue ying ji li hai xia
zhong guo ri bao wang huan qiu zai xian xiao xi
rui shi fei xing yuan yi fu
luo xi zhong yu cheng gong shi xian le er shi de meng xiang
xiang niao er yi yang zi you ao xiang zai tian kong
tong shi ta ye chuang zao le ren lei hang kong shi shang de you yi ge qi ji
luo xi shen bei yi fu pen qi dong li yi
cheng gong fei yue ying ji li hai xia
cheng wei hang kong shi shang di yi ge fei yue hai xia de ren ti zhi sheng ji
dang tian luo xi bei zhuo ta de tan xian wei dong li yi
cheng zuo yi jia qing xing fei ji cong fa guo bei bu jia lai shi sheng kong
fei ji pan dao
de gao du shi
ta dian ran le an zhuang zai dong li yi xia fang de
ge xiao xing pen qi yin qing
ran hou tiao chu fei ji
dong li yi de liang yi zai fei ji li shi shou qi de
luo xi tiao chu fei ji hou
la dong yi ge sheng zi
zhan kai liang yi

pan jie bing fei guo lao si
sui ran shi fou guo lao si shang wu ding lun
dan pan jie de bing shi huan qi ren men dui bai ling gong zuo qiang du he jian kang zhuang kuang de guan qie yu fan si
si da ban gong shi ban ye jing chang deng huo tong ming bing bu wei qi
ye nei jing zheng ji lie
da jia dou lai zi ming xiao

you xiao xi cheng jin nian chu

dui yu zhong zhong luan xiang
zheng fu san ling wu shen
hu nan sheng jiao yu ting jin zhi zai zhi jiao shi dui ben xiao ji xian ren jiao xue duan de xue sheng jin xing you chang jia jiao
jiao yu bu chu tai
zhong xiao xue jiao shi zhi ye dao de gui fan
yao qiu jiao shi zi jue di zhi you chang jia jiao
chang sha shi jiao yu ju gui ding
gong ban jiao shi zai pei xun ji gou jian zhi jiang xia ke
jiu kai chu xiao zhang
gong ban xue xiao jiao shi bu de ti min ban pei xun ji gou jin xing xuan chuan
fa dong he zu zhi sheng yuan
si da ming xiao dai tou cheng nuo
cong dang nian qi
bu gao jia jiao
suo you zai zhi jiao shi bu dao xiao wai jian zhi jian ke
bu tui jian pei xun ji gou
min jin chang sha shi wei geng shi zai
nian de ti an zhong yan ci tong chi jiao shi hui kou feng
guan yu jia qiang dui wo shi min ban xue xiao bian xiang gei zhong xiao xue sheng zeng jia fu dan de jian guan de jian yi
ti an zhong ren wei
ying yan jin min ban xue xiao
han min ban bu xi xue xiao
zhao shou zai xiao xue sheng jin xing wen hua ke bu xi
dui jie shao xue sheng dao min ban xue xiao bu xi wen hua ke er na hui kou de jiao shi
an jie shou shang ye hui lu chu li
dan zhe shi yi chang mei you jin tou de mao shu you xi
chang sha bu ke de feng qi yi jing xing cheng
chu zhong you de ban ji da ban ge ban shen zhi quan ban xue sheng
dou zai can jia ge zhong xing shi de bu ke
bu can jia hui bei qu xiao
xue sheng geng yuan yi zai zi ji xue xiao bu ke
ji yuan yi jie ke
shen zhi mian fei
dan zhe zhong dai yu zhi you gao san nian ji cai neng xiang shou
qi yu zhi neng xuan ze shi chang
jiao yu bu men zai jin zhi cheng jian zhi bu ke shi
lao shi jiu rang xue sheng hua zheng wei ling
zhuan tou duo jia pei xun xue xiao
yu pei xun xue xiao chu xian mao dun le
jiao shi jiu zi ban bu ke ban
dang cha jin feng sheng jin shi
jiao shi you he pei xun ji gou he zuo
hu nan jiao yu jie ren shi ren wei
chang sha zhi suo yi sheng xing bu xi ban xian xiang
chu le jin qian li yi wai
ye he hu nan de sheng xue jing zheng yi chang can lie you guan
lao shi tui jian xue sheng qu pei xun xue xiao
hen da cheng du shang shi yin wei que shi ke yi ti gao cheng ji
ying shi jiao yu dui xue sheng zuo ti de ji qiao xing yao qiu fei chang gao
ti gao zuo ti de shu lian cheng du he ji qiao
dui kao shi you hen da de bang zhu

bi bi jie shi
zhi yu xue sheng

de xue sheng gen ben bu xiang bu
ze fa zi nei xin xiang bu ke
ya li zhong xue gao san xue sheng shuo
chang jun he ya li shi si dui tou
bu bu ke hui luo ren yi jie
geng you hu nan shi da fu zhong de xue sheng
yin wei zi ji suo zai de xue xiao gui ding bu bu ke
jiu tou su qi ta bu ke de xue xiao
ta zai wang shang fa tie cheng
gei bie ren xue xiao duo yi tiao sheng lu
jiu deng yu duo gei wo men yi tiao si lu
wo men bu bu cheng
qi ta xue xiao ye bie xiang bu
wo men na qi shou zhong di dian hua
qu xiang mei ti fan ying
xiang sheng ting fan ying
jia jing pin kun de hai zi zai zhe chang bi pin zi yuan de sai pao zhong diao le dui

gei ta men da guo zhe

yi ge an zi
