ta zai zheng ci zhong shuo
yi ge duo yue hou
deng xiu qiong jiu gao su ta you le shen yun
zi ren wei gen ta de guan xi yi ban
bu shi zhen de zhong yi ta
zui you xin fu li de bing bu shi ta de bian jie
ta zai fan dian shang ban
mang zhe shi cai cai gou he qi ta shi qing
dian xiao ye san chang
dou you shi jian zheng ren
ta de tong shi huan yuan yi zheng ming
gong zuo ze ren xin qiang
geng bu shi luan lai de ren
lian ma jiang dou bu hui da
bao xian jing ji lin xue quan ye bei huai yi guo
nian jiu ren shi le deng xiu qiong
mai guo duo fen bao xian gei ta
ceng jian shi shi zong zhi hou
ta ji ci chu ru ceng jia yu deng xiu qiong jian mian
ta zai fa xian shi ti de dang tian jiu bei jing cha zhao qu wen hua
dan shi xun su zai jing fang zhe li xi tuo xian yi
er qie cheng le you li zheng ren
ta zai hou lai de zheng ci zhong shuo
deng xiu qiong da dian hua jiao ta dao jia li qu
gao su ta hai zi bu shi ceng jian shi de
hai gao su ta
ceng jian shi de si shi mei mei deng yan ping de lao gong zuo de
jiang an mian yao fang zai tang li gei ta he le
zai qu jiu dian chi fan
zai ba ta tui xia shui
nian hou ben kan ji zhe zai zhao dao lin xue quan
zi ji yi jing bu ji de dang nian de xi jie le
ta ji de de shi
you yi ci wo qu jian guo deng xiu qiong yi hou
jing cha jiu zhao le wo qu
shuo deng xiu qiong shuo de
ming an gen wo you guan
wo shuo mei ke neng de
jing fang jiu rang wo bang zhu ta men liao jie da ting qing kuang
wo zi ji ye hao qi zhe ge shi qing
suo yi qu zhao deng xiu qiong wen de bi jiao duo
zui hou de mu biao suo ding le mao ding gao
ri bei xing ju
bi deng xiu qiong wan ban ge yue
yan ge shuo qi lai
mao ding gao bing bu shi deng yan ping de zhang fu
nian you le ge nv er
dan mei you na guo jie hun zheng
mao ding gao ye shi yang shan ren
yu ceng jian shi tong sui
jia ren ru jin dou zai fo shan
ta chu er chuo xue hou zai guang zhou de yi jia mian bu chang gong zuo le ji nian
zai tang xia kai guo
nian fu zhuang pei liao dian
nian hui yang shan zuo guo
nian yao cai sheng yi
zhi hou yi zhi zai fo shan si zhi wei lu jiu huo shi chang zuo er shou jia dian sheng yi
ta duo ci dao guo hua du
ceng gai shi hui yi shuo
chi zhu dou zai wo di di jia li
hao duo ren kan jian guo
wo jian guo hao ji ci
jing fang de tu po xing jin zhan zai
deng xiu qiong bei zhua de di san tian
zhe yi tian de kou gong bi lu
deng xiu qiong de tai du tu ran ni zhuan
qian ban duan hai zai kang ju
ni xian zai dou you zheng ju la
ti wo qu qiang bi la
wo you jiang shen me
you shen me hao jiang
hou ban duan tu ran hen pei he
zuo le xiang xi de you zui gong shu
hai xie le yi fen qin bi gong ci
ban ben shi mao ding gao zhao ceng jian shi ji ci jie qian bu cheng
jiu jiao suo ta sha fu pian bao
ta ze shi hen zhang fu chu qu piao chang
re le xing bing chuan gei guo ta yi ci
ta zhao ren mai le an mian yao
mao ding gao jiang
li an mian yao mo cheng fen
fang zai cha shui li gei ceng jian shi he le
ta men zai chu men dao bi cun lu kou de feng ze yuan can guan chi fan
fan hou mao ding gao kai zhuo mo tuo che ba ceng jian shi zai zou
lian ren dai che tui xia yu tang
guan jian zheng ren zhu yi yun de zheng ci
ta shi feng ze yuan can ting de fu wu yuan
zai bi lu zhong xiang xi hui yi le
ri xia wu suo jian de qing xing
mao ding gao he bao zhuo hai zi de deng xiu qiong xian dao
zai le yuan bao fang zuo xia dian le cai
ran hou mao ding gao chu qu jie le yi ge nan ren
zhe ge ren lai de shi hou jiu xiang he zui le
yi zhi zai sha fa shang shui jiao
shen me ye mei you chi
da gai ban ge duo xiao shi hou
ta men jie zhang yao zou
ta hai bang mang ba ren tai dao mo tuo che shang
ge ren yi qi zuo na liang hei se nv shi mo tuo che li kai
mao ding gao kai che
deng xiu qiong he hai zi zuo hou mian
yi zhi mei xing de ceng jian shi zuo qian mian
zhe ji ge ren zhu yi yun yi qian dou bu ren shi
dan zai yi ge duo yue hou tong guo bian ren zhao pian
ta que zhi ren chu le suo you de ren
er qie xi jie feng fu dao ta men dian de cai
liang gua niu rou he suan rong cai xin
ta ti gong le yi ge jie shi
na tian gang hao shi ta yi ma dong ju xiang guo sheng ri
zai feng ze yuan de tao yuan fang qing ke
ta kan dao le yuan fang de nan nv qing nian dian de liang gua niu rou mei zen me chi guo
hai xiang na dao yi ma na jian fang qu
yin wei yi ma na bian shi da huo guo
cai mei you na
suo yi ji de hen qing chu

ta dang tian zuo che dao hua du

hou lai de yi ge wan shang

ta zai fa ting shang ye shi zhe me chen shu de

da hu yuan wang

tong yang bu da suan fang qi de hai you deng yan ping
ta man fu wei qu
jue de zi ji de jing li yi jing ke yi xie yi ben shu
ta hui bi deng xiu qiong er zi de xue yuan guan xi
ye hui bi deng xiu qiong ji ci tuo ren gou mai an mian yao de yi wen
zhi shuo zi ji bu zhi dao
ta zui tong hen de ren
shi bao xian jing ji lin xue quan
ta yan zhong de lin xue quan
ju xin po ce
zai ceng jian shi si hou ceng jing zhao jie jie deng xiu qiong suo yao
li you shi ke yi bang ta bai ping ci shi
zai an juan cai liao zhong
chu le deng xiu qiong de gong shu
ta de yi ge jie fu ye ti gong le zheng ci
da yi shi deng xiu qiong gen ta zi xun guo
shuo lin xue quan zhao ta yao
gen ju hai zi sheng fu xu rong de zheng ci
ceng jian shi que ren si wang hou
lin xue quan ji ci yue ta jian mian
tan qi le hai zi de shi
shuo chi zao hui huai yi dao ta tou shang
jin qi bu yao gen deng xiu qiong lian xi
lin xue quan de xing wei
kan qi lai di que you xie qi guai
nian guang zhou shi zhong yuan chong shen de shi hou
ye zhao ta liao jie guo qing kuang
ta dui fa yuan de shuo fa ye ji lu zai an
da yi shi ta shi ti gong an ban shi de
shi gong an she le quan tao rang ta pian qu deng xiu qiong de xin ren
qu tao ta de hua
wan yuan de bao xian li pei cong lai mei you zhi fu guo
deng yan ping hou lai da dian hua cha guo jie jie de bao dan
yi wai de zhi
yue sheng xia de

shi lin xue quan ban li de
ta xiang bu tong
na shi hou wo jie jie ren dou bei guan zhuo
lin xue quan zen me neng qu de shou quan
tui de bao fei qu le na li
zai zhao dao lin xue quan
ta yi jing hen bu yuan yi zai hui yi zhe xie shi qing
shen zhi hen duo xi jie dou bu ji de le
dan dui yu tui bao de shi qing
ta hen que ding
shi deng xiu qiong shou quan gei ta de

ta tai du jian jue di fa shi zi ji jue dui mei you qiao zha guo
yi qie xing wei dou shi ge ren hao qi he ti jing fang ban shi
ta ye bu cheng ren jian guo hai zi sheng fu xu rong
ta de yan zhi zao zao
ting qi lai hao xiang ye hen you ku zhong
wo zhi dao ta men yi jia ren dou hen si wo
shuo wo hei xin
ke wo mei shuo jia hua
wo ye shi zai bu xiang zai chan he dao zhe ge shi qing li
ta bei wu zui fang chu lai de shi hou
wo dou hen dan xin ta hui bao fu wo
wo na li na guo ta de
ta mai de zui hou yi fen bao xian
gei ta er zi mai de
ji qian kuai qian hai shi wo dian de
ta shuo di er tian jiu gei wo
jie guo yi zhi mei you gei

zui hou de pan jue jie guo
ta men ye shi kan bao zhi cai zhi dao de
ta men de mu qin

nian shi jian li

xin fang zi hai zai jian
shi gong sheng long long zuo xiang
ceng jian shi de si
yi jing man man dan cheng le yi ge gu shi
zhi qing huo zhe bu zhi qing de ren
dou you ge zi de ban ben
ceng jian shi de na yi ban wu zi zu le chu qu
ta na liang yue
de hei se mo tuo che
da lao chu lai zhi hou hai neng yong
ta de di di yi zhi qi dao xian zai
zhe liang che ting zai ceng deng xian de tang wu li
ye shi wang shi de zheng ming
pan dian zhong guo chuan tong xiao qian
gu qin kun qu he xiang ru xuan fei yi
shen me ren wan shen me niao
wu da lang zhi neng wan ma que
shang mian zhe ju da shi hua ke neng zhao zhi xin zuo pai de pao hong
dan wu fa gai bian de shi shi shi
zhong guo ren que shi shi hen hui wan de
luan shi ye wan
ju shuo zui hui wan de zu qun shi ba qi zi di
jia wu nian gen xiao ri ben gan zhang shi
ba qi jun jie le sheng zhi hou hao hao dang dang chu zheng
long qi piao piao de dui wu li jiu you ti long jia niao de zhu er
lao she bi xia de ren wu
ye jue dui bu shi wu zhong sheng you
kan le ta xie de jing cheng ren wu
jiu zhi dao jiu zhong guo de qi shu
zai wan de guo cheng zhong man man hao jin
zhong guo ren hui wan
ye gei zhong guo wen hua liu xia le wu bi feng fu
wa jue bu jin de yi chan
jin ge er de fei yi
ji ben shang dou shi wan chu lai de
zai shuo wo men wan shen me

chi bao le he zu le shou li you ji ge ding dang xiang de

zai kan kan xing san yu shi jie ge guo de hua ren da ma jiang
hua hua sheng yi zhi jing dong zhuo wai guo de yue liang
zai shuo jin de ba
jiao yi wu cheng le she hui kai ming de xiang zheng
lao bai xing chun jiang shui nuan
hen kuai zhi qi le ma jiang zhuo
jie zhe shi shou lu ji
cong dan la ba wan dao si la ba ji hu yi lu kuai jin
bing xing bu bei de shi lu xiang ji
zhe wan yi er da da ci ji le dao ban de ying shi zhi pin

ran hou wan qi le ka la

dou li you liang qian de kai shi wan gu dong
na ge shi qing nao da le

que ling you yi fan shen yi
re ai chuan tong wen hua

suo xing de shi shang hai yin yue xue yuan liu xia le dai xiao lian
dan yi shi mei you ke cheng she zhi
ta zhi neng zai tu shu guan zi liao shi gei chang pian bian mu lu
zhe yi gan jiu shi

ta zai xiao kan fa biao le yi pian lun wen

zai he bei sheng xing tang xian de chang tu ke yun zhan
ren he yi wei ben di ren
dou shuo de chu zhang jian xia jia de ju ti wei zhi
zhang jian xia jiang
de gan zang yi zhi gei huan bing de gong gong hou
ta jiu cheng le dang di de ming ren
yi ge er xi fu
neng ba zi ji de gan juan gei gong gong
zhe shi duo da de xiao xing a
zhe yang de hai zi
xian zai neng you ji ge
xiang qin men ti dao ta
yi lian sheng di dou shi kua jiang
wo men yi jia ren dou shi zhi xing zi
xing tang xian long zhou zhen xi guan cun shi ge cheng zhong cun
zhang jian xia yi jia jing ying de lv guan zuo luo yu cun li wei yi de gan dao shang
ji zhe lai dao zhang jian xia jia shi
ta zheng zai chu fang li mang zhe zhang luo yi jia ren de wu fan
wu fan de zhu shi shi hong zao zhou
yi zhi chi zhe ge
ping chang ye yong hong zao ao shui he
chi wan wu fan hou
zhang jian xia you gan zhuo song xiao xue yi nian ji de er zi shang xue
zai yu ji zhe jian mian de zui chu yi xiao shi li
ta ji hu mei shi jian he ji zhe shuo shang ji ju hua
nian chu sheng de zhang jian xia shi zhe ge si shi tong tang jia ting li de chang xi
jia zhong chu le ta hai you po po de mu qin
er zi wu kou ren
gong gong jin nian nian chu yi jing guo shi
song hai zi shang xue
zhao gu dian li
li li wai wai yi dui shi er
yi dian er xian gong fu mei you
zai ji zhe kan lai
zhang jian xia de chuan zhuo hen shi mao
pu tong hua ye shi fen biao zhun
ta xiao zhuo gao su ji zhe
zi ji jie hun qian hen mian tian
dou bu gan gen mo sheng ren shuo hua
dou shi zhe ji nian zai lv guan li bang mang duan lian chu lai de
huan jing gai bian ren bei
zhang jian xia jing ren jie shao ren shi le zhang fu wang liang
wo men lia ke yi shuo shi yi jian zhong qing
ge yue bu dao jiu jie hun le
yu zhang jian xia jia pu tong de jia jing xiang bi
wang jia tiao jian bu cuo
gong gong wang zhen long yi qian shi cheng bao gong cheng de
jia li hai zai jing ying yi jia lv guan
zhang jian xia shuo
po jia cong lai mei you qiao bu qi ta
ta zai hun hou hen kuai rong ru le zhe ge jia ting
wo men yi jia ren dou shi zhi xing zi
you shen me hua jiu shuo chu lai
mei nao guo mao dun
jiu suan xia bu lai shou shu tai ye bu hou hui
yue jie hun de
dang shi wo gong gong jiu shi zhong du gan ying hua
zhang jian xia hui yi dao
gong gong de bing qing kai shi e hua
ci hou jiu yi zhi zhan zhuan ge di qiu yi
you bing ren de jia ting
qi fen shi hen ya yi de
zhi dao wo men de er zi chu sheng
jia li cai you le yi dian huan le
zhang jian xia shuo
gong gong bei que zhen wei gan ai
zai zhong guo ren min jie fang jun
yi yuan kan bing
yi sheng jian yi gan yi zhi
dang shi shi gan te bie shao
gong gong de bing qing you hen jin ji
jiu da suan zuo huo ti gan yi zhi
xue ye jian cha de jie guo gei ta men liu xia le yi xian xi wang
sui ran wang zhen long de qi zi he liang ge er zi dou shi
dan zhang jian xia shi
he gong gong de xue xing yi yang
wo gong gong hai you
dan shi ta men shen ti dou bu hao
ji shi neng yong
ren jia ye dou ge zi cheng jia
you zi nv le
ye de wei ren jia zhuo xiang
wo jiu gen zhang fu shuo
zhang jian xia de jian yi zao dao le quan jia de ji lie fan dui
yi xiang ge xing gang qiang
ji ji pei he zhi liao de wang zhen long shen zhi jue ding fang qi zhi liao
gong gong gen wo shuo
tian di xia mei you zhe yang de shi qing
ru guo zhen yao na yang de hua
wo men wang jia jiu tai dui bu qi ni le
zhe ge bing wo ning ke bu zhi
wu lun zen me quan shuo
wang zhen long dou jian jue bu tong yi
shen zhi yi jian dao zhang jian xia jiu sheng qi
rang ta chu qu
yan kan zhuo gong gong de bing qing yi tian tian e hua
xin ji ru fen de zhang jian xia
xiang dao yong ji jiang fa lai shuo fu gong gong
yi tian xia wu
zhang jian xia dai zhuo
sui de er zi qu yi yuan kan wang gong gong
ta kan zhuo hai zi jiu tou tou di ca yan lei
neng zhi hao de bing
yi hou zhe hai zi jiu mei ye ye le
nin zai ye jian bu dao sun zi le
zai si xiang dou zheng le
wang zhen long zhong yu tong yi jie shou gan yi zhi shou shu
yi sheng tou tou ba zhang jian xia jiao dao ban gong shi
xiang xi di jie shuo le shou shu ke neng cun zai de feng xian
yi sheng shen zhi gao su ta
ru guo xian zai hou hui
ke yi ma shang bang ta zhao ge yi xue jie kou jiao ting shou shu
er qie jue dui bao mi
jiu suan xia bu lai shou shu tai
wo ye bu hou hui
wo zhe ge ren jiu shi zhe yang
shuo dao zuo dao
zhang jian xia bei tui shang le shou shu tai
shou shu cong zao shang
dian yi zhi zuo dao wan shang
zai zhang jian xia shen shang yong yuan di liu xia le yi dao
ren zui shao liu xia
de gan zang jiu ke yi zheng chang sheng huo
yi sheng gen ju wo gong gong de qing kuang
yi zhi le wo
shu hou di san tian
wang zhen long gang neng xia chuang
jiu zai qi zi de chan fu xia qu kan er xi fu
wo shuo wo hai mei qu kan nin ne
zen me nin xian lai kan wo le
ta yi jian wo jiu ku le
wo de ming shi ni gei de a
zhang fu xian zai dou bu gan qu wo fu mu jia
zhang jian xia mei gan ba zi ji yao gei gong gong yi zhi gan zang de shi qing gao su fu mu
shou shu qian zhi shuo shi qu bei jing zhao gu gong gong
rang ta men bang mang zhao kan hai zi
zuo wan shou shu gang gang
dian ji zhuo jia zhong lao xiao de zhang jian xia bian jian chi chu yuan
xian hui niang jia kan kan
ba shi qing gao su fu mu
na shi wo yi xia zi shou le
zou lu hai zou bu tai wen dang
wo ba zhe shi gen fu mu shuo le yi hou
ta men shen me ye mei shuo
jiu rang wo hui po jia le
zhang jian xia yue xiang yue bu dui
ba ma zen me shen me dou mei shuo ne
wo jiu gan mang you hui le tang niang jia
dao jia yi kan
fu mu yi jing quan dou shuo bu chu hua le
yi ye zhi jian
ta men ba sang zi dou ku ya le
wo cong xiao dao da ji hu mei sheng guo shen me bing
shen ti te bie hao
kan zhuo huo beng luan tiao de yi ge gui nv nong dao zou lu dou yao ren fu
neng bu nan guo
kan zhuo qiao cui de qi zi
zhang jian xia de zhang fu you xin teng you kui jiu
bu shan yan ci de ta
zhuan men lai dao yue fu mu jia
yi jin men jiu gui xia lai
er gang hui jia zhu le
zhang jian xia jiu yin wei shou shu yin qi de dan lou you zhu jin le yi yuan
chuan le yi gen dan guan wang wai dao dan zhi
dan guan zai liang gen lei gu zhi jian chuan jin qu
ya po shen jing
teng de dou bu gan hu xi
hou lai dan guan tuo luo
kai shi chong xi fu qiang
tie mo guo min cha dian yao le ming
qian hou jin le san ci yi yuan
zao de zui jiu bie ti le
liang ge duo yue hou
zhang jian xia he gong gong zhong yu xian hou kang fu chu yuan
qi shi dao xian zai
wo fu mu ye mei zhuan guo zhe ge wan lai
ta men jue de juan gan ke yi
dan yi kai shi bu ying gai man zhuo ta men
wan yi nv er jiu zhe me mei le
ta men lian zui hou yi mian dou jian bu dao
suo yi wo zhang fu xian zai dou bu gan qu wo fu mu jia
wo xian zai bu shi ting hao de
zhe ge le guan de nv zi
shuo qi zhe xie shi
yi zhi le he he de
wo men de ba jia kang qi lai
zhu yuan qi jian
zhang jian xia juan gan jiu gong gong de shi qing bei yi jia mei ti bao dao chu lai
hen kuai jiu chuan bian le zheng ge xing tang xian
you ren shuo shi po jia bi zhuo wo zuo de
ye you shuo wo gong gong tai zi si de
hai you ren gen wo fu mu shuo
ni gui nv huo bu liao ji nian le
wo jiu gen jia li ren shuo
ren jia ai shuo shen me shuo shen me
zhang jian xia huo da di xiao le
hai shi hao ren duo
hen duo mo sheng ren zhuan men pao dao wo jia lv guan lai kan wo
hai you ren gei wo xie shi
zhang jian xia de xing wei gan dong le xu duo ren
que zui zhong mei neng wan hui gong gong de sheng ming
jin nian nian chu
wang zhen long de bing qing zai du e hua
er du gan yi zhi hou zhen jun gan ran bu zhi shen wang
gong gong yi zou
gan jue jia li yi xia zi kong le
wo men ba po po de mu qin jie lai
gen wo men yi qi zhu
hao rang po po xin li hao guo yi dian
gong gong zai de shi hou
jia li de shi qing dou shi ta zuo zhu
xian zai gong gong zou le
wo men de ba jia kang qi lai
wei le gei gong gong zhi bing
ji nian xia lai
jia li hua le shang bai wan
jia jing ri jian shuai luo bu shuo
hai qian xia le bu shao wai zhai
wei le zhuan qian
zhang jian xia liang kou zi shen me zheng qian jiu gan shen me
zhe xie nian chu le sheng bing de shi hou
zheng tian dou zai mang
ji zhe dui zhang jian xia shuo
ta you dian xiang dian shi ju
li si qin gao wa yan de na ge jing ming
gan lian de er nai nai
na ke bi bu liao
zhang jian xia shuang lang di xiao qi lai
dan xian ran ta dui zhe ge ping jia hen man yi
wo dao shi fei chang xi huan er nai nai
na ge dian shi ju wo kan le hao ji bian
zhang jian xia de gan zang yi jing hui fu dao liao yuan lai de
chang hui yuan lai de da xiao shi bu ke neng le
zhang jian xia shuo
qian ji tian zai zhong hua xin er shi si xiao de ping xuan huo dong shang
zhang jian xia yu dao le yi ge juan gan gei mu qin de nv hai
ta zuo wan shou shu
xian zai hui fu de hen hao
kan zhuo ta wo ye geng you xin xin le
zhang jian xia ba san ceng lou de lv guan chong xin zhuang xiu
xian zai sheng yi hai bu cuo
wo yi dian er ye bu chou
wo men hai nian qing
zhi yao ren jian kang
sheng huo jiu you xi wang
sui lao tai yao jin yu le quan dang ming xing yin zheng yi
sui de lao tai tai
ren sheng yi jing jin ru le dao ji shi
dan ta jing ran kai shi le wei ming xing meng xiang de fen dou
ru guo wo men tan tao she hui xue
sui lao tai tai yao zuo ming xing de meng xiang shi yi ge ji qi ju you ji ji yi yi de hua ti
dan shi hui gui ta sheng huo de ben lai mian mu
jie he ta de jia ting bei jing

yi ge ren ying gai fu chu shen me dai jia
dong fang wei shi
dong fang zhi bo shi
sui lao tai yao jin yu le quan dang ming xing
yi xia wei jie mu shi lu
quan fang wei zong guan zhe ge she hui
yao dang ming xing de da ti shang dou shi nian qing ren de shi qing
huo zhe shi nian qing jun nan mei nv men de zhu yao shi qing
ni wu fa xiang xiang
sui de lao tai tai
ren sheng yi jing jin ru le dao ji shi

wei ni jie shi yi ge bu tong fan xiang de lao tai
wo geng gu du
er qie te bie de jian ku
chi jin le ren jian de ku
shou jin le ren jian de zui

wo yao yao ya zou yi hui
wo jiu rang zhe zhong xin nian
mo mo di zhi chi wo
du guo le zhe ge liu nian
wo de jia shi bu neng hui qu
bu neng li kai shen zhen de
ren de yi sheng
yi ding yao you yi ge li xiang
you ge fen dou mu biao
fan zheng wo jiu cong xiao jiu shi te bie xi huan chang ge
wo jiu zhe yi ge ai hao
ping sheng jiu zhe me yi ge ai hao
dan shi wo mei you lai de ji wa jue
jiu zai jia li zuo yi ge jia ting zhu fu
cheng tian wei zhuo guo tai zhuan
jiu shi wei ta men zuo fan
jiu zai zhe ji shi ping fang mi de wu li zhuan
deng wo lao nian le
wo de er sun man tang le
jia ting sheng huo ye hao le
wo jue de wo dui jia zuo chu de feng xian
yi jing ke yi le
suo yi wo jiu qiu ni men
gen jia ting shuo
qiu ni men gei wo dian shi jian
gei wo ge ji hui
rang wo chu qu chuang dang chuang dang
wo yi jing dao ji shi le
wo yao wei wo zi ji huo yi ba le
suo yi wo hen jian jue
wo bu neng hui qu
sui lao tai jia jie de yi duan zhen qing gao bai
wen ting zhe wu bu wei zhi dong rong
ye xu bu shao ren jin jin ren wei zhe ge lao tai yin wei
sui le yao zuo ming xing de xing wei hen ling lei
shi ge ling lei de lao tai er yi
dan shi shui you neng nai xia xin lai qing ting ta de xin ling hu sheng ne
dong fang zhi bo shi
bian lun jia bin bai xu xu liang guan dian xian ming di shuo dao
zai jia jie a yi he ta zhang fu zhi jian
ni jue de ta men liang ge ren shui geng you wen ti
wo ren wei zai zhe ge nian ji
neng you zhe yang de meng xiang zhui qiu
shi zhi de gu li de shi qing
dan shi wo xi wang
liang wei ru guo you zhong jian zhe zhong de fang fa
liang wei neng bu dao zhao de dao
wo wen de wen ti hen jian dan
dui yu yi ge nv ren lai jiang
shen me jiao fu ze ren
wo jue de zhong guo you tai duo de nv xing
cong lai mei you de dao guo ji hui
wei zi ji fu ze ren
suo yi wo jue de ta shi yi ge wei zi ji fu ze de nv ren
wo men ying gai gei ta zhang sheng
wo men kan zhe qi jie mu de suo you guan zhong
wu lun ni shi zhang fu
hai shi er zi
ni dou yao wen yi xia ni de qi zi huo zhe mu qin
ta hai you shen me li xiang mei you shi xian
you qi shi qi zi nian qing shi hou de meng xiang
shi bu shi hai mei you shi xian
yi ding yao xiang fang she fa zhi chi ni de qi zi huo zhe mu qin
rang ta wei zhe ge li xiang qu fen dou yi ba
wei zhe ge meng xiang qu nu li yi ba
bu guan neng bu neng shi xian
zong gui yao gei ta yi ge shi xian de ji hui
bie rang ta lian qu nu li yi ba de ji hui dou mei you
ta yi qian wei he mei you qu nu li
yin wei ta wei le xiang fu
ye wei le jiao zi
ta xi sheng le zi ji suo you ceng jing yong you de nian qing zi ben
ni men ying gai wei ta xi sheng yi ba le
sui de jia jie a yi
shi ru he zai wei zi ji de meng xiang er nu li de
dong fang wei shi
dong fang zhi bo shi
nan zi jiang shu ju bao tao shui huo jiang
yuan jing guo yi zao diao nan jiang shang su
jian xi ji zhe zhao yun long fa zi he nan luo yang
sui de ren le liang zhang xiang pu tong
mian se you hei
zai luo yang huo che zhan jian mian shi
ji zhe hen nan zai ren qun zhong jiang ta ren chu
dan jiu shi zhe yang yi ge pu tong ren
que yin wei yi chang guan si ming yang quan guo
yin suo yao fa piao zao ju
ta xiang luo yang shi xi gong qu guo shui ju ju bao le luo yang shi sai bo shu ma cheng shang hu de zhe yi xing wei
gai shang hu bei chu fa
ren le liang ze yin ju bao you gong huo xi gong qu guo shui ju yi yuan jiang li
gan jue shou dao wu ru de ren le liang jiang xi gong qu guo shui ju gao shang fa ting
yao qiu qi chong xin zuo chu jiang li
dan shi bai su
gai an chu shen jie shu hou
ji zhe zai luo yang cai fang le ren le liang
ta gao su ji zhe
ta jing chang wei le wei quan er da guan si
xi gong qu guo shui ju hen ke neng yi wei ta shi da jia zhuan ye hu
yi yuan jiang li shi gu yi diao nan ta
hua fei shu bai yuan ju bao shang jia
bei jiang li yi yuan
wei suo yao fa piao
ren le liang xiang guo shui bu men ju bao luo yang shi sai bo shu ma cheng shang hu
wei ci lai hui pao le san tang xi gong qu guo shui ju
you ci chan sheng de wu gong fei he che fei da shu bai yuan
dan ta zui zhong de dao de shi guo shui ju yi yuan jiang li
zhe ling ta ku xiao bu de
ji nan shi bao
ni wei shen me ju bao sai bo shu ma cheng shang hu
wo zai na er hua
yuan mai le ge dian nao yi
hou lai gan jue yi zi you dian er ce wai
jiu na hui qu xiu li
jie guo dian fang zhi gei dian le ke luo si jiu shuo xiu wan le
wo bu man yi
ta men shuo mei you fa piao bu gei huan
ji nan shi bao
mai yi zi de shi hou ni mei yao fa piao ma
dan ta men zhi gei le yi zhang shou ju
wo yao huan huo de shi hou
xiang rang ta men gei wo bu kai fa piao
ta men que shuo yao bu jiao
yuan qian cai neng kai
wo jue de bu he li
jiu mei jiao zhe
ji nan shi bao
ni xiang guo shui bu men ju bao shi wei le suo yao fa piao
fou ze yi zi jiu mei fa huan
re xian xiang guo shui bu men tou su
xi gong qu guo shui ju gong zuo ren yuan bu jiu jiu da lai dian hua gen wo liao jie qing kuang

zheng ge ju bao guo cheng shun li ma
bu zen me shun li
guo le liang san tian

bing ba gou wu shou ju de fu yin jian jiao shang
wo zhao ban le

wo you song qu le

ta men shuo shang hu na bian bu cheng ren zhe shi
yao wo qu dang mian gen shang hu dui zhi

ni qu le ma
qing kuang shi fou shu shi
ying gai shi guo shui bu men ren ding a
za neng rang tou su ren he bei tou su dan wei jian mian dui zhi ne
ji nan shi bao
ni zui zhong na dao fa piao le ma
wo zai ji tian hou shou dao yi ge kuai jian
li mian you liang zhang yi bai yuan mian zhi de fa piao
hai you yi zhang ju bao ling jiang tong zhi shu
dan jiang li shu e zhi you
guo shui ju ning yuan gao jia da guan si
ye bu yuan jiang li ju bao ren
ren le liang ren wei yi yuan jiang li shi dui ta de wu ru
ta wei ci jiang xi gong qu guo shui ju gao shang le fa ting
yao qiu chong xin zuo chu jiang li
er ta ting shuo dui fang hua
yuan qing luo yang zhi ming lv shi lai da zhe chang guan si
ta men ning yuan gao jia qing lv shi

zhe rang wo wu fa li jie
ji nan shi bao
na dao zhe yi yuan qian ling jiang dan shi shi shen me gan jue
wo dang shi dou bu gan xiang xin
you dian er shou dao wu ru de gan jue
shen bian de peng you zhi dao yi hou ye jue de bu ke si yi
ji nan shi bao
ni zai zhe jian shi shang hao fei jing li da ma
jia shang zhong jian deng dai de shi jian
cha bu duo you liang ge xing qi
guo shui ju mei ci dou shi zai gong zuo ri da dian hua rang wo guo qu
wo wei ci qing jia san ci
jiao tong fei ye hua le ji shi yuan qian
hai you shou ju de fu yin fei
jia qi lai da gai hua le liu qi bai yuan
ji nan shi bao
shi bu shi ren wei de bu chang shi
wo ren wei xi gong qu guo shui ju zhe yang zuo da ya le ju bao ren de ji ji xing
wo xiang tao ge shuo fa
jiu ba ta men gao shang le fa ting
ji nan shi bao
qing lv shi le ma
zai luo yang qing ge hao yi dian er de lv shi cha bu duo yao hua shang qian yuan qian
wo fu dan bu qi
ji nan shi bao
xi gong qu guo shui ju qing lv shi le ma
wei le da ying zhe chang guan si
xi gong qu guo shui ju hua
yuan qing le luo yang de zhi ming lv shi
zhe rang wo wu fa li jie
ta men ning yuan gao jia qing lv shi
ye bu yuan zai chu qian jiang li ju bao ren
xi huan da wei quan guan si dan bu kao zhe ge zhuan qian
zai ren le liang da guo de wei quan guan si zhong
bu shao zhi ming qi ye cheng wei bei gao
you ren zhi yi ta shi kao da guan si zhuan qu pei chang de da jia zhuan ye hu
ren le liang yu yi fou ren
ji nan shi bao
zai wang shang sou suo ni de ming zi
sou dao hen duo fen pan jue shu
bei gao fen bie shi mao tai jiu chang
zheng zhou dan ni si sheng huo guang chang luo yang fen gong si
luo yang shi jin guan yan jing gong si he zheng zhou yue jia shang ye you xian gong si luo yang xin du hui dian
yuan gao yi lan dou shi ni de ming zi
ni di que qi su guo yi shang zhe xie shang jia he dan wei ma
dou shi wo qi su de
ji nan shi bao
qi su zhe xie gong si dou shi yin wei shen me
ju ti ji bu tai qing le
you xie shi wo shou dao shang jia jia ge qi zha
you xie shi chan pin zhi liang you wen ti
ji nan shi bao
zui hou zhe xie an zi de jie guo ru he
you ying ye you shu ba
ji nan shi bao
wang shang you ren shuo ni zhuan men kao da wei quan guan si zhuan qu pei chang
gen ben bu shi
wo wei quan bu shi wei le zhuan qian
wo shi ge jiao zhen de ren
fa lv yi shi ye bi jiao qiang
peng jian bu gong ping de shi jiu xiang yao ge shuo fa
er qie wo da di na xie wei quan guan si dou bu shi yi suo pei wei mu di
ji nan shi bao
ting shuo ni you shi hai yao kui qian
wei shen me yao jian chi wei quan
ru guo zi ji de quan yi shou dao le qin hai
jiu de tong guo fa lv tu jing tao ge gong dao
ji nan shi bao
ping shi you gong zuo ma
shou ru ru he
wo cong shi fu wu ye gong zuo
shou ru hai ke yi
mei ge yue you liang san qian yuan ba
ji nan shi bao
ni qing jia chu lai da guan si
ling dao zhi chi ma
ting zhi chi de
mei ci qing jia da guan si
ling dao dou mei zu nao guo
ji nan shi bao
bang shen bian de peng you da guo wei quan guan si ma
you shi gei peng you bang mang
you shi bang peng you de peng you da guan si
huai yi guo shui ju gu yi diao nan hai hui shang su
xi gong qu guo shui ju zai fa ting shang biao shi
gen ju xiang guan gui ding
dui ju bao ren de jiang li biao zhun yi ban shi shou jiao ru ku shu e de qian fen zhi wu
xi gong qu guo shui ju chu fa shang jia
ying jiang li ju bao ren
suo yi yi yuan jiang li bing bu wei gui
dan ren le liang huai yi guo shui ju zhe shi gu yi diao nan
hai yao shang su
ji nan shi bao
ni qu ling guo shui ju de yi yuan jiang li le ma
ru guo qu ling
lu fei qi ma de ji kuai qian
ling le zhe yi yuan qian wo xin li ken ding hui bie qu
ji nan shi bao
dan xi gong qu guo shui ju ren wei yi yuan jiang li shi fu he gui ding de
xi gong qu guo shui ju fa le shu ma cheng shang hu
shu yu di e du de chu fa
shang hu jiang le wo
ye shi di e du de jiang li
zhe zhong zuo fa ji qi bu dao zhen she shang jia de zuo yong
ye biao da bu liao dui ju bao zhe de gu li
wo shen zhi huai yi ta men shi zai da ya ju bao ren de ji ji xing
ji nan shi bao
ni huai yi xi gong qu guo shui ju gu yi gei ni yi yuan jiang li
ta men hen ke neng ye ting shuo guo wo xi huan wei quan
ren wei wo shi diao min
jiu gu yi yong yi yuan jiang li lai diao nan wo
ji nan shi bao
zhi qian hai you ren yin ju bao huo jiang ma
ta men de jiang jin shi duo shao
wo jiang dan shang de biao hao shi
suan xia lai wo ying gai shi xi gong qu guo shui ju jin nian di
ge ji yu jiang li de ren
wo qi su yi hou
jin nian di yi ge de jiang de ren lai zhao guo wo
gao su wo ta dang shi de le
yuan qian de jiang li
ji nan shi bao
ta dang shi shi shen me qing kuang
ye shi ju bao wei quan
xi gong qu guo shui ju dui shang jia fa kuan
dan ta ye yi zhi mei qu ling
ji nan shi bao

wo yi ding yao tao ge shuo fa
ji nan shi bao
zhe ci qing lv shi ma
ying gai hai shi bu hui qing
fei yong tai gao le
ji nan shi bao
ru guo hai bai su
hai hui ji xu shang su xia qu ma
na wo ying gai bu hui zai shang su le
fou ze hua de qian geng duo
ru guo zai ci bai su
dui wo shi ge hen da de da ji
ji nan shi bao
yi hou zai yu dao bu gong ping de shi
hai hui ji xu wei quan ma
wo hai hui jian chi wei quan
zhe shi ken ding de
nan zi wang shang gu xiong sha qin die yin suo yao
wan yuan zuo sheng yi wei guo
zhong yang dian shi tai
jin ri shuo fa
xiang guan hua ti tao lun qing guan zhu
jin ri shuo fa
xin lang wei bo
cun min jia zhong tu ran yu xi an qing pu shuo mi li
shou hai ren lao yu jin nian
zai dang di jing ying yi jia er shou feng ren ji chang
zhe shi yi jia zuo fang shi de gong chang zui li mian de shi che jian he cang ku jin ai da men de liang jian wu zi
qi zhong yi jian zuo wei ban gong he hui ke yong
ling yi jian ju zhu dang tian bang wan an fa shi chang zi yi jing xia ban lao yu shi du zi dai zai ban gong shi li de
hou lai ju shou hai ren lao yu miao shu dang shi ta zheng zuo zai dian nao qian bei dui zhuo men kou wan dou di zhu you xi
zhe shi jin lai yi ge nian qing ren wen ta shi bu shi yu lao ban
zai de dao ken ding de da fu hou na ren you xun wen feng ren ji de jia ge
lao yu guang gu zhuo wan you xi hai mei lai de ji zhuan shen kan dao dui fang de lian jiu tu ran gan dao bei bu yi zhen ju tong
na ge mo sheng de nian qing ren yi jing na dao bu duan di ci xiang le ta
lao yu da sheng hu jiu xiong shou hen kuai tao li
you yu shi qing shang lao yu bu jiu jiu quan yu chu yuan le
ta bu yuan yi mian dui jing tou jiang shu na tian zao yu de xi jie
ta de qi zi ye hen bu qing yuan di jie shou cai fang
ta qi zi shuo zhe ge an zi bei zhen po yi hou ta men yi jia ren jiu zai ye bu yuan yi ti qi you guan zhe ge an jian de ren he shi qing le
ta men shen zhi fei chang hai pa lin ju men yi ju bu jing yi de xun wen shen zhi yi ge tan xun de yan shen
na me dao di shi shen me yuan yin rang zhe jia ren you le zhe zhong bu yuan yi hui shou
shen zhi nan yi qi chi de ku zhong ne
dang tian an fa hou gan lai de min jing dui xian chang jin xing le zi xi di kan cha
xian chang mei you xian suo po an jiu zhi hao jie zhu dui zhou bian de zou fang
you cun min fan ying shuo zhi qian de yi duan shi jian fu jin ceng jing chu xian guo you wai di kou yin de ren xiang ta men da ting lao yu jia de qing kuang
wen guo lao yu jia qing kuang de ren bu zhi yi ge
yan jiu an qing jing fang zai an jian zhong ke yi ken ding de yi dian shi shou hai ren yu xiong shou bing bu xiang shi
zhi yu xiong shou wei shen me yao jia hai lao yu
an zhao chang li fen xi zhi shi zhe hen ke neng shi chu yu mou zhong sheng yi shang huo zhe sheng huo shang de jiu fen
gen lao yu you bu ke tiao he de mao dun de ren
er lao yu gen qi zi si qian xiang hou jue de zi ji ping shi yu ren wei shan bu ke neng de zui xia shen me ren jie xia zhe yang de shen chou da hen
shi jie shang mei you wu yuan wu gu de ai
ye mei you wu yuan wu gu de hen
hen ming xian zhe ge xiong shou jiu shi chong zhuo lao yu qu de
ta wei shen me yao dui lao yu xia shou ne
jiu zai ban an ren yuan mei you zhao dao geng xin de xian suo yi chou mo zhan de shi hou lao yu jia you chu shi le
xing xiong zhe tao zhi yao yao chi dao ren zai ci shang men
si wo tou cun de cun zhu ren da le ge dian hua shuo yu mou jia you jin qu ren le
dang shi wo ma shang dai min jing bu dao
fen zhong de shi jian dao liao yu mou jia zhong
zai ta wu li tou kun zhuo yi ge
lai sui de xiao huo zi
bei zhua zhu de zhe ge ren lao yu de qi zi ren wei ke neng jiu shi xiong shou
yin wei zai ci zhi qian lao yu hai mei chu shi er de shi hou ta jiu jian guo ci ren
lao yu de jia li an zhuang you jian kong qi
ci qian jiu ceng jing pai dao guo zhe ge xiao huo zi
suo yi zhe ge xiao huo zi zai lao yu yi jing chu shi hou you lai le da jia jiu zhua zhu le ta
bei zhua huo de ren jiao song yang wei
ta shen shang ju ran jiu cang zhuo xiong qi
kan lai ta zhen you ke neng jiu shi xiong shou
sui shan xi chang zhi ren
ta shuo ta dai zhuo dao zi shi yao dui fu lao yu de
dan shi ta hai mei you dong shou
ta dui jing fang jiao dai ta shi zai wang ba shang wang shi fa xian le yi ge jie shao zhuan qian de tie zi
fa tie de ren wang ming jiao lang
zai gen zhe ge lang lian xi shi lang zai wang shang shuo xiang bu xiang lai dian ci ji de wo zhe li you shi qing
song yang wei de wang ming jiao zhi shui ta wen shen me shi qing
lang shuo gei liang ge ren fang xue
ren yao shi sha si le jiu gei
song yang wei de xia yi ju wen hua shi zai yi fen zhong zhi hou
zhe shuo ming ta bing bu shi mei you you yu de
song yang wei gan guo yi xie xiao de huai shi zhe hui ke shi yao qu sha ren
song yang wei wen ren zai na li
lang shuo zai he bei qing xian de yi ge cun zi li
lang suo shuo de he bei qing xian de zhe dui fu fu jiu shi lao yu he ta de qi zi
wan yuan de you huo zhi xia song yang wei dong le xin kan le tie zi yi ge yue li ta xian hou liang ci lai qing xian cai guo dian
dang ta di san ci zai qu lao yu jia shi bei fa xian bing bei zhua zhu le
song yang wei ba gu yong ta zhe ge ren gei ta fa de suo you de duan xin quan bao cun zhuo
shi yi ge hen chang
de shi jian duan
yue fen yi zhi dao fa sheng zhe ge an zi chu xi
ri dang tian dou you duan xin
jing guo zi xi xun wen jing fang que ren song yang wei bing bu shi
ri an jian de xiong shou
na me zhen xiong shi shui ne
shi na ge lang hai shi bie de shen me ren ne
jing fang sui ji zhuo shou xun zhao wang shang de zhe tou e lang
dan shi lang de xiu jue fang fu hen ling min
ta hao xiang zhi dao song yang wei chu shi le zai wang shang tu ran xiao shi le
liao tian qi de tou xiang shi hui se de hen chang shi jian ye bu zai deng lu le
na me jiu mei you ban fa zai zhao dao zhe tou e lang le ma
zhe shi ge ji shu nan ti qing xian gong an ju xin xi qing bao zhong dui ye yi ji ri di gong zuo le
tian zhang wo le lang de ling sui xin xi
tong guo wang luo hen kuai jiu zhao dao le lang de zong ji
ta cang zai shan dong ji nan shi de yi ge ju min xiao qu li
ta de zhen ming jiao li dong yu ji lin sheng chang chun shi ren zai ji nan shi kai le yi jia xiao dian zuo sheng yi
lang gen lao yu you shen me chou yao dui ta xing xiong ne
xun wen de jie guo rang jing fang ji qi yi wai lang ju ran bing bu ren shi lao yu fu fu
ta ye shi zai wang shang jie dao de bie ren jie shao de sheng yi
wan yuan mai lao yu fu fu de ming
li dong yu jue de zhe shi yi dan da sheng yi
dan shi yi zi ji de neng li ta zuo bu liao zhe ge shi qing yu shi jiu gan qi le zhong jie de mai mai
jing fang quan li zhui bu
fan zui xian yi ren lu xu luo wang
lang shuo ta cong wang shang zhao dao de xia jia wang ming shi zhi shui
ta da ying zhi shui shi er ban cheng le gei
er zhi shui jiu shi qian mian bei zhua huo de na ge song yang wei
lang li dong yu de gong shu yu zhi shui song yang wei de kou gong shi fen wen he
dan zhi shui song yang wei bing bu shi xiong shou xing xiong zhe lang shuo ta ye bu zhi dao dan shi shi zhen de ru ci ma
zai shen xun de tong shi jing fang xiang xi tiao qu le lang zai ban nian zhi nei liu xia de suo you wang luo hen ji
jing fang fa xian zai zhe duan shi jian li wei le wen tuo di zheng dao zhong jie fei lang suo lian xi de xia jia chu le zhi shui song yang wei hai you yi ge wang ming jiao zuo
shen xun zai chi xu dan shi lang yi kou yao ding ta zhi gen song yang wei lian xi guo hai mei dong shou er lao yu shi bei shui suo shang ta yi gai bu zhi
jing fang de zhe zhao qiao shan zhen hu qi le zuo yong lang de zui zhong yu bei qiao kai le

dan shi lang de shou xuan jiu shi

lang dang shi gen
xu nuo shuo gan cheng zhi hou de bao chou shi
jiu hui hua shuo yi jing dong shou le
dan ta zhi dong le yi ge ren

zai zhe zhong qing kuang xia lang you zhao dao le zhi shui
you ding le xie yi rang ta qu dui lao yu liang kou zi di er ci xing xiong
jing fang zhen cha dao liao
zai yi wu de yi jia bin guan nei bei jing fang zhua huo
zhen ming lin jian jun zhe jiang sheng lin an shi ren
ju ran shuo ta ye bu shi dui lao yu dong shou de ren
ta cong lang na li jie dao huo hou you zhao dao le wang you jiao gu hun de
wan rang gu hun qu gan zhe jian shi qing
na me zuo an de zhen xiong shi bu shi jiu ke yi ren ding jiu shi zhe ge gu hun le ne
jing fang hou lai de zhen cha zheng shi le zhe yi dian wei le na
wan kuai qian gu hun zhen shi sha fei ku xin
ta pa liu xia xian suo zuo huo che dao liao cang zhou hou ying shi cong cang zhou huo che zhan zou le
gong li zou dao liao qing xian si wo tou cun lao yu jia
xing xiong zhi hou ju ran you zou hui le huo che zhan
bi xu yao zhua huo gu hun
dan shi gu hun xian zai ta piao zai na er ne
dan zuo an zhi hou lang mei gei
zi ran ye jiu gei bu liao gu hun qian
sui ran qian mei na dao shou dan shi jin shen de gu hun ye li ke cang qi le zi ji de xing zong
hao ma he shou ji hao ma dou ting yong le
dan shi ta bing mei you neng tao tuo zhui bu
yi ge yue hou
ri gu hun zai wang shang fu huo de na yi tian ta bei qing xian jing fang cong xi an de wang ba li qin huo le
gu hun zi ji ren wei ta zuo de tian yi wu feng wo men ba ta dai dao che shang zhi hou dang shi ta tai du fei chang qiang ying
zhen cha yuan shuo wo men shi he bei jing fang de dao xi an lai zhua ni
ni zi ji xin li yao qing chu

ni bie shuo le
ji ran ni men da lao yuan de neng zhao dao wo shuo ming ni men yi jing zhang wo le wo
gu hun luo wang you lang zhong jie gu yong xia jia
xia jia zai gu yong xia jia de xing xiong xian suo zong suan shi qing chu le
xian zai zhi you zui hou de yi ge wen ti le lang zhi shi zhong jie ta shi cong yi ge wang ming jiao dan yi de shang jia shou li jie de huo na me zhe ge zui shang jia dan yi shi shui
ta gen lao yu fu fu you shen me yang de shen chou da hen yao hua
wan yuan mai ta men de ming ne
an qing jie zhen xiang da bai gu xiong zhe jing shi qin sheng er zi
lao yu jin nian
sui yi bei zi sheng huo zai qing xian de si wo tou cun
ta ji hu bu shang wang ta men jia dao shi you dian nao dan shi na ge dian nao shi yong lai da you xi de
lao yu wu fa xiang xiang yi qun wang luo shang de wu he zhi zhong yi yi zhong ta gen ben bu ke neng cai dao de fang shi zu he qi lai yao ba ta zhi yu si di
xian zai jing fang tong guo wang luo shang de zhu si ma ji ba yi ge yi ge de xia jia dou zhao dao le na me zhao dao zui zhong fa bao de na ge shang jia
ye zhi shi ge shi jian wen ti dan dang zhen xiang da bai de shi hou shi suo you ren da gan yi wai de shi hou
na ge zui zhong de shang jia shi shui ne
jing fang zhao lai zhao qu zhao le ban nian zhen zheng xiang yao lao yu ming de ju ran shi ta de qin sheng er zi
yuan lai lao yu gen ta de qian qi you ge er zi jiao yu zeng hui
yu zeng hui cheng ren ta jiu shi zai wang luo shang gu xiong sha ren de zui shang xian dan yi
wei shen me yu zeng hui hui dui sheng shen fu qin zuo chu zhe yang de shi qing lai ne
shi bu shi zuo fu qin de yi qian you shen me shi rang er zi jue de te bie wu fa rong ren ne
ju liao jie zai yu zeng hui
sui de shi hou lao yu gen qi zi li hun
na ge shi hou er zi de cheng zhang gang gang jin ru le qing chun qi
li hun ben shen dui hai zi shi yi zhong shang hai er qie zai li hun hou fu qin dui yu zeng hui de guan xin jiu geng tan bu shang le
xian zai lao yu shuo qi yi qian bu zai er zi shen bian de na xie nian dui hai zi de leng luo yan yu zhi jian shi you hui guo zhi yi de
dan shi er zi dui fu qin zai bu man zui zhong zen me jiu bian cheng le bu gong dai tian de chou hen le ne
yu zeng hui de ji mu shuo zhe shi you
wan yuan yin qi de
zai sheng mu bing si zhi hou yu zeng hui hui dao le fu qin de shen bian
ta cong fu qin na li yao le
wan yuan lai kai le ge wang ba
you yu shu yu guan li yu zeng hui de wang ba mei duo jiu jiu dao bi le

hou lai yu zeng hui you yi ci xiang fu qin yao
wan yuan qu zuo sheng yi lao yu jiu mei you da ying
da xue tuan wei fu shu ji tiao lou zi sha xing ge zheng zhi lv zao bu gong dai yu
he fei gong ye da xue tuan wei fu shu ji chen gang tiao lou si le
dang chen gang zi sha de xiao xi chuan kai shi
suo you shu xi ta de ren dou yi wei zhe shi yu ren jie qian de yi ci e zuo ju
shui ye bu hui jiang zi sha gen he gong da zui nian qing de fu chu ji gan bu lian xi zai yi qi

shuang shou ping fang
zhe ge bei xu duo ren jie du wei shi zong shen yi yue
lin ran fu si de zi shi
qian yi tian de shang wu
he gong da tuan wei shu ji de jing pin jie guo chu lu
yi zhi bei ren wai jie kan hao de chen gang yi wai luo xuan
zhong zhong ji xiang biao ming
jing xuan tuan wei shu ji de shi bai bu guo shi ya kua ta de zui hou yi gen dao cao
ta you zhe you lai yi jiu de yu ji yu fen nu
yi ci zhi zai bi dei de yan jiang
yi ge pu tong de zao chen
qi zi li zhi hui mu song chen gang chu men shi
ting jian ta yi lu heng zhuo xiao qu
qu ben fu yi chang jue ding ta ren sheng ming yun de yan jiang da bian
dui yu zhe wei mei you ren he bei jing de fu chu ji gan bu lai shuo
yan jiang ji hu shi ta ren wei sheng qian shi zui gong ping de you xi gui ze

chen gang dou zai yan jiang huan jie sheng chu
zui zhong de yi dang xuan
zai zhe ci tuan wei shu ji de xuan ba zhong
ta yi wei zhe tao you xi gui ze yi ran shi yong
jin nian chun jie zhi hou de ji hu mei tian wan shang
mo ni yan jiang jiu xiang xi fang ren fan qian de dao gao yi yang
cheng wei zhe ge jia ting wan fan hou de bi bei yi shi
zhi yao wang xia zhai de ke ting zhong yang yi zhan
chen gang hen rong yi jin ru zhuang tai
jia ru wo dang shang tuan wei shu ji
wo yi ding hui
zuo zai sha fa shang de qi zi li zhi hui

ta zui wai xiang
you yu zai zhong xue cheng ji yi zhi ming lie qian mao
lao shi jing chang la ta zai quan xiao da hui shang gen tong xue men jiang zen me ba cheng ji gao hao

ji hua xing bi ni qiang
chen gang de tong xue ba chen gang de da xue si nian cheng wei ku nan de li cheng
yi dao wan shang
chen gang de da xue tong xue men zai su she da pai hun ri zi
chen gang que yao deng tong xue men shui jiao le cai hui lai

chen gang bu shi chu qu zuo jia jiao zheng sheng huo fei
jiu shi dai zai xue sheng hui
mei ci kai xue
ta du hui cong jia dai yi da bao de jian bing he xian cai lai zuo huo shi
dan ta cong bu man yuan
fan dao jing chang gei tong xue men gu jin er
bei guan jue wang wu ji yu shi
zong hui you chu lu de
ta de yi wei shi you hui yi
wo men jing chang he ta kai wan xiao shuo
ni de hua bi si xiang jiao yu ke you xiao guo
ta re ai xue sheng hui de gong zuo
ceng gao su ta di jie jie chen fang
zai xue sheng hui duan lian shi wei le gong zuo hou ke yi jin kuai shi ying huan jing
zhao yi fen wen ding de gong zuo
rang bie ren kan de qi
zai chen fang de ji yi zhong
di di cong bu bao yuan ming yun bu gong
jing chang nian dao yi ju hua shi
guo qu shu yu si shen
wei lai shu yu zi ji
guo jia yi bu zai bao fen pei
ta cheng le xi li shao shu ji ming neng liu xiao gong zuo de jiao jiao zhe
zhou wei de tong xue dou kan hao ta chu se de gong zuo neng li
ren wei ta tian sheng jiu shi chi zhe wan wan fan de
wei lai mei zhun neng zuo ge fu xiao zhang
ci hou liu xiao shi san nian
ta ji hu hen kuai jiu shi ying gao xiao de zhe tao you xi gui ze
bing qie ru yu de shui
ji hu mei yi bu dou you ta jing xin gui hua de hen ji
zai ji suan ji xue yuan zuo fu dao yuan
jiu shun dai du le ge ji suan ji shuo shi
nian dao tuan wei dang le fu shu ji
ta jiu nian le ge guan li xue bo shi
zhe yang ke yi yun yong dao xing zheng gong zuo zhong qu
ta ceng gao su yi wei xiao you
chen gang de chuang tou yi ban bai zhuo liang lei shu
yi shi yong lai kao yan
xie lun wen yong de gong ju shu
er shi mao ze dong
li jia cheng zhe lei ren wu zhuan ji
li zhi hui you shi kan xie wen xue lei de shu
hai bei ta qu xiao shuo shi tai xiao zi qing huai
zi da qu nian di he gong da di si lun zhong ceng gan bu xuan ba de xiao xi gong bu yi lai
suo you jian dao chen gang de ren dou shuo
zhe ge zhi wei fei ta mo shu
zai tong shi de yin xiang zhong
chen gang hen shou ling dao qi zhong
ling dao jiao dai ta yi jian shi
ta bu jin xiang hao zen me zuo
er qie ma shang qu zuo
ta de yi wei tong shi shuo
tan kai chen gang de lv li
si hu hen nan zhao dao di er ge dui shou
zai tuan wei san nian zhong liang ci nian du kao he you xiu
an hui sheng she hui shi jian xian jin ge ren
yue dao dong nan da xue gua zhi xue gong bu fu bu zhang
zai wai ren kan lai geng shi hui lai sheng qian de qian zou
jiu lian zhe ci bao ming jing xuan tuan wei shu ji de shi hou
ta de yi wei jing zheng dui shou chen wen en ye shuo
wo lai gei ni re shi le
li zhi hui hui yi
chen gang dui zhe wei he gong da xin xiao qu guan wei hui ban gong shi zhu ren bing bu mo sheng
nian tuan wei fu shu ji de xuan ba zhong
chen wen en bei chen gang ji bai
sui ran li zhi hui ye ou er ting chen gang ti qi chen wen en shi xiao zhang de ren
dan chen gang jian xin zu zhi hui ren ren wei xian
bing bu shi shu bu qi
zai qi zi li zhi hui he tong shi men de ji yi zhong
mei dang ta men kua chen gang sheng li zai wang de shi hou
chen gang zong shi xiao he he di qian xu qi lai
zhi dao chen gang chu shi zhi hou
qi zi li zhi hui meng de yi qi zhe yi mu
cai zhi dao zhe ju hua po you yi wei
chen gang ke neng yi zhi wu fa bai tuo san nian ping bu shang fu gao de yin ying
zai li zhi hui de yin xiang zhong
qu nian xia tian de di san ci jing xuan fu jiao shou zhi cheng luo bai shi chen gang zui jue wang de shi hou
li zhi hui zhi jin ji de chen gang tang zai sha fa shang shi wang de biao qing
wu xu cong shi jiao xue he xue shu yan jiu gong zuo
xue li yi ran ru jin gu
tao zai chen gang zhe lei gao xiao xing zheng ren yuan de tou shang
zai he gong da zhe lun ren shi jing pin zhong
chu le tuan wei zhi wai
zhu ru dang wei xue gong bu chang
dang wei tong zhan bu chang deng dang kou xing zheng zhi wu
jun xu yao ju you gao ji zhuan ye ji shu zhi wu
zhi cheng de gao di yu shou ru gua gou
yi wei he gong da de lao shi shuo
yi ge fu chu
ru guo mei you fu gao zhi cheng
yi ge yue zhi neng na dao
dan ru guo ping shang fu gao jiu bu yi yang le
yi ju yi wang chen gang yuan du fu shu de ge xing
li zhi hui qing chu
zhang fu shi wang de bu shi shu bu qi
er shi you xi gui ze mei you yi ge liang hua de zhi biao
yi nian yi ge yang
rang ta kan bu dao wei lai
xue xiao po ge ti ba ta ru wei
zui hou sui ran shu le
dan ta ren le
chen gang shi ge dong de zhi zu de ren
li zhi hui dui nv er guan jiao tai yan
chen gang chang chang quan ta fang shou
mei ge ren dou you zi ji de ming yun
wo xiao de shi hou jue de neng dang wo men cun li de dian gong jiu hen hao le
di er nian shu diao shi yin wei ling dao gen chen gang ti qian da le zhao hu
ni men hai nian qing
neng bu neng xian rang gei nian ji da yi dian de lao tong zhi
li zhi hui ji de chen gang dang shi ye mei shen me yuan yan
xin xiang fan zheng hai nian qing
you de shi ji hui
dan dao liao di san ci
sheng chu zhe jing ran shi yi ge wu lun xue shu cheng guo hai shi gong zuo jing li dou mei you chen gang you xiu de nv fu dao yuan
zhe rang tong yang zai jiao yu xi tong gong zuo de li zhi hui
ye hen nan jie shou
wo gen chen gang shuo
zhao zhe yang de hua
mei you guan xi
dao si ye ping bu shang
zhi dao zhang fu tian sheng ge xing yao qiang
li zhi hui hai shi quan ta
yao bu yi hou ye zhao zhao guan xi
dan chen gang shuo ta zuo bu lai
wo jiu bu xiang xin
zuo shi qing de ren de bu dao ren ke
zai qi zi yan zhong
chen gang fan shi dou you yuan ze he di xian
you ci gen tong xue yi qi qu
chen gang kan dao you tong xue hai jiao le
xiao jie zuo pei
hui lai jiu gen li zhi hui shuo
zhe zhong ren bu zhi de jiao wang
zai da xue de shi hou bu shi zhe yang de
zai she hui shang zen me bian cheng zhe yang le
li zhi hui you shi hou ling kou kai de da yi dian
ni shi lao shi
ni bu neng chuan zhe yang
hun la long guan xi de fan ju
chen gang ye si hu bing bu shan chang he xi huan
chu fei shi wei na ge lao shi song xing huo shi wei xue xiao de shi qing
yi ban de ying chou ta hen shao can jia
dou shi hui jia pei qi zi
yi xie tong xue ju hui shang
you tong xue bao yuan gong zuo zuo de zai hao ling dao dou bu xi huan
you ren hui chu xie ren zhi chang qing de dian zi
bi ru guo jie de shi hou gei ling dao song song li
dan chen gang zong shi wang zheng dao shang xiang
ning ke huan zhuo gen ling dao
ye bu ying gai yong wai zhao me
chen gang de yi wei tong xue ren wei zheng shi zhe yang de xing ge dao zhi ta zi sha
yi ge zun shou gui ze de ren fu chu na me duo
ru guo mei you hui bao
na ta bi ran hui fei chang ju sang
jie hun shi nian
li zhi hui qing chu zhi dao chen gang dui xue xiao you zhe zong jiao ban de xin ren
hen shao xi xing yu se de chen gang
zhi yao yi tan dao xue xiao
yan li zong hui shan chu shen shen de man zu
ta ye hui gen qi zi bao yuan yi xia xue xiao de feng qi bu hao
li zhi hui jiu quan ta
ni bu yao ba shi qing xiang de na me mei hao
you xie shi qing
bu shi ni you neng li gai bian de
chen gang di er ci jing pin fu gao shi li hou
ceng ting cong peng you de jian yi
xiang shen qing dao xian li gua zhi zuo fu xian zhang
dan hou lai xue xiao pai ta qu dong da gua zhi de ji hua
you chong xin dian ran le ta de xi wang
jin nian nian chu
zai an hui sheng tuan sheng wei de gong kai xuan ba zhong
chen gang zhong yin zhun bei cang cu er luo xuan
dan hui lai hou hao wu yuan yan
li zhi hui ren wei zhang fu qi shi shi ge shu de qi de ren
zhi yao da jia dou shi an zhuo gui ze lai
dan bing fei mei ci xuan ba dou you chen gang gen zhong di gui ze
yue zhe lun tuan wei shu ji de jing xuan zhong
chen gang sui ran zai yan jiang da bian zhong you huo de di yi ming
xiao fang yi wai zeng jia le qun zhong ping yi huan jie

na shi chen gang hai mei you yi shi dao ta jiang luo bai
zhi ming de jing xuan
di er ci tu ran zeng jia de qun zhong ping yi huan jie
dui yu chen gang reng ran mei you gou cheng tai da wei xie
kao zhuo zai xue xiao
nian lai ji zan xia de hao ren yuan
zai san wei hou xuan ren zhong
chen gang yi ran huo de di yi

gen ju li zhi hui de hui yi
zhe tian zhong wu

tuan wei shu ji fu shu ji
xue gong bu tuan wei yan gong bu san ge dan wei suo you ren yuan
jin xing hua piao wu ji ming tui jian
chen gang de shou ji sheng ci qi bi fu
yi xie si jiao bu cuo de tong shi jian yi ta ye la la piao
ni zhen dan ding
ni de dui shou yi jing ba dian hua da dao wo de shou ji shang la

dang shi lai zhi jian zheng zai wu zhou chuang ban wu zhou shi dian zi gong ye xue xiao
na shi zheng shi lai zhi jian zai wu zhou zui huo de shi hou
ta shou chuang de ding dan ban xue
xi yin le da pi xue sheng
bao ming xi wang ru du gai xiao de xue sheng ren shu zui duo shi you
zhe yi shou chuang de mo shi cheng wei gui dong nan di qu zhi ye jiao yu de yi da pin pai
lai ben ren ye yin wei wei dang di jiao yu shi ye zuo chu de tu chu gong xian
bei tui xuan wei wu zhou shi ren da chang wei hui wei yuan
sui zhe quan guo zhi ye jiao yu zheng ce de bian ge
wu zhou shi dian zi gong ye xue xiao zai nan jiang lin
guo jia zhi ye jiao yu fu pin ji hua chu tai
ji hua zhong gui ding le dui pin kun jia ting zhi xiao xue sheng de bu zhu biao zhun
mei ge yue bu zhu sheng huo fei
ji hu yu ci tong shi
guang xi zi zhi qu de san nian zhi ye jiao yu gong jian gui hua chu tai
gui hua yao qiu
ge shi xian dou yao chuang li zi ji de zhi ye jiao yu zhong xin
zheng ce shi hao de
dao liao di fang jiu bian wei le
wu zhou shi dian zi gong ye xue xiao zhu guan zhao sheng gong zuo de chang wu fu xiao zhang li xu shi shuo
wu zhou shi ge xian shi jiao yu ju yao qiu chu zhong bi ye sheng chu qu kao ru gao zhong de xue sheng wai
bi xu chu ju zhi ye jiao yu zhong xin de bao ming zheng ming cai neng na dao chu zhong bi ye zheng
sheng yuan shi chang bei yan zhong gan rao he feng suo
zhao sheng de shu liang
ye cheng wei kao he dang di guan yuan de yi ge zheng ji biao zhun
yi ge xian de zhi ye jiao yu zhong xin zhu ren wang wang shi zhe ge xian de xian zhang jian ren
lai zhi jian shuo
zhe shi de wu zhou shi dian zi gong ye xue xiao shou dao yan zhong ying xiang
sheng yuan ji jin ku jie
nian jian cheng de hong ling xin xiao qu bei po xian zhi
wu zhou shi dian zi gong ye xue xiao zhi zhao dao liao
yin wei dui ban xue kun jing de zhu duo si kao
zuo wei xue xiao fu ze ren he tou zi ren de lai zhi jian jie shou le zhong xin she guang xi fen she de cai fang
zhe ci cai fang bei xie cheng nei can
fa gei le wu zhou shi si da ling dao ban zi
ben xiang tong guo nei can jie jue wen ti de lai zhi jian mei you xiang dao
zhe pian nei can rang dang di de mou xie ling dao bu man
zai sheng yuan bu ji
si mian chu ge
zi jin jin zhang de qing kuang xia

zai xue xiao mei you fa sheng zhe xie shi zhi qian
wo he tan qing yi zhi shi peng you
ta zuo mei ti
you hen duo peng you

wan yuan ben xi

an zhao dang shi wo men de jie kuan xie yi

hou lai gun dao liao

zhe yi xiao xiao de ju dong

fa zhi zhou mo
an zhao zui gao fa yuan de xiang guan gui ding

gong wu yuan lu qu zhe bei yi wu bao kao zi ge fu ze guan yuan zhi wen ji zhe
nan fang nong cun bao xun
ji zhe chen quan run
wang zhuo yin you qi ming zi de yi fen gong wu yuan kao shi cheng ji pai ming dan
huang ri bao jin jin di yao zhuo zui chun
ta gao su nan fang nong cun bao ji zhe
zhen xiang ba zhe zhang cheng ji dan si lan
huang ri bao de fen nu lai zi cheng ji dan shang de ling yi ge ming zi
huang ri bao he zhou xiao cheng tong wei
nian fen bie bi ye yu guang dong sheng nong gong shang zhi ye ji shu xue yuan he guang dong xin an zhi ye ji shu xue yuan
huang ri bao cheng wei lei zhou shi ke lu zhen ji sheng fu wu suo de yi ming si ji
zhou xiao cheng jiang qi dang an cong xue xiao qian ru lei zhou shi ren shi bu men
bing he ji jia zhen gong xiao she jian li qi lao dong guan xi

dan qu nian de yi ci gong wu yuan kao shi
que jiang ta men la che dao yi qi
wei le neng gou qiang dao jin fan wan
yi chang zheng duo zai er ren zhi jian zhan kai
luo bang kao sheng bu fu jie guo
zai guang dong sheng wei zu zhi bu he sheng ren li zi yuan he she hui bao zhang ting tong yi an pai xia
zhan jiang shi cong xiang zhen qi shi ye dan wei gong zuo ren yuan zhong zhao lu yi pi gong wu yuan
gen ju xiang guan wen jian

nian de zai zhi ren yuan

nian de zai zhi ren yuan

nian de pin yong ren yuan

fen de cheng ji

er huang ri bao ze yi bi shi
fen de cheng ji pai ming di er
ming luo sun shan
dan huang ri bao bing bu ren ke zhe yi jie guo

huang ri bao jiang wen ti fan ying dao lei zhou shi ji wei

hai feng yi jiu
er qiang chai jiang ju zhong di cun luo fei xu
zheng zai jian zheng zhong guo nong di zhi du bian ge de jin cheng
fu jia zi di yu da che xing zou ban ge zhong guo
tian dian fu xu duo guan nian
yi ge kai zhuo jia zhi yi bai duo wan hao hua che de fu jia zi di
tu fa qi xiang
dao gao su gong lu kou da che xing zou ban ge zhong guo
tian de lv cheng dian fu le ta ting guo de hen duo jiao hui
ben bao ji zhe zhang guo shi xi sheng liu ya nan
kai zhuo zi jia yi bai duo wan de hao hua qi che dou feng shi
wu da wei ji hu cong mei zhu yi guo lu bian shi tu da che de ren
ji shi kan dao
ta ye hui hao bu you yu di hu xiao er guo
zhi dao you yi tian
yi zhen tou nao fa re zhi hou
sui de tian jin ke ji da xue xue sheng wu da wei jue ding ye qu da yi hui bian che
zhe ge shen gao
dun de da kuai tou shi zai
ri qing chen chu fa de
ta bei le zu you
gong jin de shui dai
zhang peng he shi wu
bao li hai you yi ta yong guo de da yin zhi
xie shang yan tu mu di di
zuo shou ju zhuo zhi pai
you shou shu qi mu zhi
ta da suan jiu kao zhe ge shou shi
tian shi jian cong tian jin da che qu kun ming
zhe shi ta cong yi ge ji lu pian li xue lai de
na bu pian zi li shuo
you xie shi xian zai bu zuo
yi bei zi dou bu hui zuo le
ta zai she jiao wang zhan shang ji lu zhe ci lv cheng
dan ping bi le ke neng xiang fu mu tong feng bao xin de hao you
dui yu zhe ge xi guan cheng fei ji chu you
yong you hang kong gong si yin ka de fu jia zi di lai shuo
fu mu suo neng xiang dao ta zui feng kuang de lv xing fang shi
cheng si le shi zuo huo che
ta men de er zi xing ge nei xiang
ping shi shen zhi shi bu gan yu ren dui shi de
lv xing cong qi dian jiu bu bei kan hao
ba wu da wei song dao di yi ge gao su lu kou de di shi si ji zhen jing zhi yu
hao xin ti xing ta bie shang le huai ren de che
ta deng le yi ge xiao shi
gu suan shang bai liang che cong shen bian jing guo
mei you yi liang ting xia
si ji men zui duo shen chu tou lai da liang yi yan
yi ge xiao shi hou
ta kai shi fa xian na ge ding dao hou nao shao de bei bao tai zhong le
sui ran xi wang tou tian dao da tai yuan
wu da wei xie zai zhi pai shang de di yi ge mu di di shi bao ding
ta dan xin xie tai yuan
si ji ke neng xian yuan
yi ge zai jia you zhan gong zuo de xiao huo zi gao su ta
qu ning xia de che ye xu jing guo bao ding
ci shi lai le liang ning xia pai zhao de huo che
wu da wei gu qi yong qi
xi li hu tu di zou dao che qian
wen zou bu zou bao ding
liang wei si ji cong tou dao jiao da liang le ta yi fan
mei zai pan wen jiu da ying ta da che
lian jia you zhan de gu niang dou gan dao yi wai
lian kua si ji xin chang hao
wu da wei lian gun dai pa di shang le fu jia shi zuo
sheng pa ta men fan hui
si ji shi yi dui zhou ye dao ban kai che de qin xiong di
zhou xing xiong di dui ta de ji hua ming que biao shi bu jie
cheng kan ta shi da xue sheng
cai gan po li
hao ren tai shao le
yi bai liang che you yi liang da ni jiu bu cuo le
zhe shi wu da wei di yi ci jie chu huo che si ji
guo qu ta kai che zou gao su gong lu shi
bu zhi ma guo duo shao man tun tun de da che
ta zhu yi dao
zhou shi xiong di chuan de hen po
bu tai wei sheng
pi xie you qi ang zang
zhi jia feng shi hei de
ta cong wei she xiang guo zi ji gen zhe yang de ren ji zai yi liang che li
cong xiao dao da
zhang bei jiao yu ta bu yao he mo sheng ren shuo hua
ta shen zhi xiang guo
jue bu zhu dong qu ce suo
wan yi zi ji xia che yi hou
che kai zou le zen me ban
er si ji xia che shi
ta ye hui gen zhe xia che
che shang fang zhuo qian
wo hai shi zhu dong dian bi jiao hao
ta zuo de shuang tui shi qu le zhi jue
si ji mei you chi fan
zhi zai ban lu mai guo yi dai gua zi
cong zao chen kai shi e zhuo du zi de wu da wei ye bu hao yi si chi
huo che dao liao bao ding
si ji dan xin ta xia che hou mei ren da li
zhi yi ba ta shao dao tai yuan
wu da wei jue de da che ren you yi wu pei si ji liao tian
jin ke neng gei ren jia jie men
ting de zui duo de

ta zhu yi dao
si ji yi du zi yi jian
shuo zhuo shuo zhuo jiu hen ji dong
ta jian guo lu pang she zhi de yi jian xiang
ke na shi ting bu jin yi jian de yi jian xiang
zhi shi yi kuai jin shu ban
zheng mian qi cheng yi jian xiang de mu yang
bei mian shi kong qi
guo shou fei zhan shi
wu da wei hui zhu dong xia che
dun de zhong liang
jin liang sheng dian fei yong
ta yu di yi liang che zai tai yuan fu jin fen shou
ta ji gan ji zhou shi xiong di de hao xin
you yin yue jue de

ke wan fan hou de yi ge duo xiao shi li
zai ye mei you yi liang che li ta
ta jiu jin zhao le jia xiao lv guan
xu yao ge an jing de di fang gei wo ma da dian hua
ta zai dian hua li pian mu qin zi ji reng zai su she
xin li que yi da qi tui tang gu

gu ku ling ding
zai qi liang de xin qing zhong

bing bu xiang zheng ming shen me

zhan zhuan tuo guan xi
zhao dao yi ge shi ye dan wei de gong zuo
mei yue ling ji bai kuai qian xin shui
ta zai na li ren shi le bi ta xiao liang sui de qu fei fei
hen kuai jiu jie le hun
wang chi chang tong guo fu qin de guan xi
jie shi le zai fo shan de shan dong lao xiang
yu shi jue xin nan xia
xi wang zai jing ji fa da di qu zuo sheng yi
tao li zhuan bu dao qian de ri zi
nian nian di zhou cheng dian kai zhang shi
zhuan rang fei he ya jin yi gong hua le san wan yuan
cha bu duo shi ta jia li de quan bu ji xu
guang fo wu jin cheng gang kai ye liang nian duo
ren liu liang shao
wei le xi yin dian pu ru zhu
zu jin jiao yi nian zeng ban nian

hao wei zhi dang kou de zhuan shou fei jiu yao

hai you wei sheng guan li fei
zhi an guan li fei

zheng zha zhe me ji nian

dan kai te di que rang geng duo de ren zhi dao le yi xie ying guo pin pai bing gou mai ta men

bi tui li qing dan bu shai chu le lai
bi qian jia zai yi qi
shi zhang xi fei shang ren jing ji he xin xi hua wei yuan hui hang ye chu fu chu zhang yi nian lai shou dao de quan bu hao chu fei
zhang xi fei zhi shi yi ge ji bie hen di de xiao li
dan xiang dui lai shuo
ta suo zai de hang ye chu que shi ge yao quan zai wo de bu men
cheng dan zhuo yan cheng ji xie
jian cai deng hang ye chan ye zheng ce de guan che yu luo shi gong zuo
yu shi qiu ren ban shi song hao chu fei
si hu cheng le yi xie ren yan zhong zai zheng chang bu guo de shi
dan zai zhang xi fei kan lai
zhe shi li yong te quan mou qu si li
dan zhen yao du jue ci shi you bu na me jian dan
you de ren zhao wo ban shi
shi ba qian jia zai cai liao dai li
dang zhe tong shi de mian bu fang bian tui

song li de ren jue de zhe si kong jian guan
mei shen me hao tui ci de
la la che che
ying xiang bu hao

bu shou qian de liu yan

zhang xi fei ye you zi ji de xiang fa

ru guo ni qiao qiao di tui
